WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:35.530
As-salamu alaykum wa rahmatullahi wa barakatuhu.

00:00:35.530 --> 00:00:57.530
As always, we commence by praising Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala, sending blessings and salutations upon Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam and all his companions.

00:00:57.530 --> 00:01:03.530
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala bless them and may He bless every single one of us and grant us all goodness. Amin.

00:01:03.530 --> 00:01:14.530
Beloved brothers and sisters in Islam, as I walked out yesterday, my young son told me that you have made a mistake. I told him what is the mistake.

00:01:14.530 --> 00:01:23.530
He says you said the Sahara Desert when it was the Arabian Desert. So I looked at him and I laughed and I said don't worry, tomorrow I will start with that slip of the tongue.

00:01:23.530 --> 00:01:33.530
When we spoke of Umayyah bin Khalaf and how Bilal ibn Rabah remembered everything that had happened and how he was dragged in the desert, it was the Arabian Desert.

00:01:33.530 --> 00:01:40.530
And I'm sure we would all have known that it was a mere slip of the tongue. May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness.

00:01:40.530 --> 00:01:46.530
The Battle of Badr, we had completed it. I just want to recap two or three points from this Battle of Badr.

00:01:46.530 --> 00:01:54.530
The Prophet ﷺ spent three days in Badr after the war. The reasons for that, so that the enemy does not come back.

00:01:54.530 --> 00:02:01.530
They had fled and some of them might decide to come back whilst the Muslims were going to Madinah Munawwarah.

00:02:01.530 --> 00:02:06.530
So one of the reasons was or to remain in Badr was to ensure that that does not happen.

00:02:06.530 --> 00:02:15.530
Secondly, to bury both sides, to bury the Muslims who had lost their lives, the 14 of those who had lost their lives,

00:02:15.530 --> 00:02:26.530
and at the same time to bury the Mushriks in a mass grave or in the pit that they were finally buried in Al-Qalib.

00:02:26.530 --> 00:02:31.530
So to bury those who were dead and those who had been martyred.

00:02:31.530 --> 00:02:43.530
The third reason was in order to gather the spoils or the booty or that which was left behind by the Kuffar of Quraish as they had departed or as they had fled.

00:02:43.530 --> 00:02:49.530
And the fourth reason was that the army needed a little bit of a rest.

00:02:49.530 --> 00:02:56.530
And what would happen is if they were to immediately move without resting, perhaps they will get tired and so on.

00:02:56.530 --> 00:03:04.530
So it served many purposes and Allah SWT had instructed Muhammad SAW to remain there for three days.

00:03:04.530 --> 00:03:09.530
Remember, whatever he did was by the instruction of Allah SWT.

00:03:09.530 --> 00:03:23.530
Thereafter, when they got to a place known as As-Safra, there was an instruction that had come from Allah SWT to divide the spoils or the booty in a specific way.

00:03:23.530 --> 00:03:34.530
However, mention must be made of the little debate that took place between some of the parties from amongst the Muslims as to what should happen with these spoils.

00:03:34.530 --> 00:03:36.530
This was the first major battle.

00:03:36.530 --> 00:03:40.530
They had had quite a lot that was left behind by the Kuffar of Quraish.

00:03:40.530 --> 00:03:47.530
And so as they were debating what should happen, Allah SWT revealed verses instructing them.

00:03:47.530 --> 00:04:14.090
They are asking you about the spoils of war.

00:04:14.090 --> 00:04:18.090
Tell them that those spoils of war belong to Allah and His messenger.

00:04:18.090 --> 00:04:20.090
Whatever they decide is final.

00:04:20.090 --> 00:04:23.090
So be conscious of Allah and sort your matter out.

00:04:23.090 --> 00:04:25.090
Don't dispute amongst each other.

00:04:25.090 --> 00:04:29.090
And remember, if you are true believers, you will follow Allah and His messenger.

00:04:29.090 --> 00:04:32.090
Those are the opening verses of Surah Al-Anfal.

00:04:32.090 --> 00:04:35.090
And we ask Allah SWT to grant us goodness.

00:04:35.090 --> 00:04:40.090
So Muhammad SAW decided that he will give everyone an equal share.

00:04:40.090 --> 00:04:53.090
And he decided to add nine of those who did not take part in the war, who had been left in Madinah Munawwarah by his instruction or who had been sent elsewhere by his instruction at that particular time.

00:04:53.090 --> 00:04:55.090
Something also very important.

00:04:55.090 --> 00:04:59.090
Two more points that I want to make mention of the Battle of Badr before we proceed.

00:04:59.090 --> 00:05:05.090
One is Mus'ab ibn Umayr radiallahu anhu had a brother of his known as Abu Azeez.

00:05:05.090 --> 00:05:10.090
And this Abu Azeez ibn Umayr, he was from amongst those who was caught.

00:05:10.090 --> 00:05:14.090
And when Mus'ab saw them taking him, he passed a comment.

00:05:14.090 --> 00:05:19.090
Before I say what he said, it's important for us to know who was Mus'ab.

00:05:19.090 --> 00:05:22.090
Once again we make mention he came from a wealthy family.

00:05:22.090 --> 00:05:28.090
He was spoiled to the degree that Rasulullah SAW says from the youngsters of Makkah,

00:05:28.090 --> 00:05:32.090
I don't know a single one who has been spoiled this much by his own mother.

00:05:32.090 --> 00:05:39.090
And when he accepted Islam, he was tied down by his mother and thereafter he was expelled, he was harmed, he was tortured.

00:05:39.090 --> 00:05:47.090
And until there came a time when his skin was flaking off and he was so poor, he didn't even have clothing, he lost his weight and so on.

00:05:47.090 --> 00:05:53.090
When Mus'ab saw his brother, who was mashallah looking quite well, but he was from amongst those who was caught.

00:05:53.090 --> 00:06:01.090
He tells the captives, you better make sure you ask for a handsome amount from this man because his folks are very wealthy.

00:06:01.090 --> 00:06:04.090
Allahu Akbar, his folks are very wealthy.

00:06:04.090 --> 00:06:16.090
May Allah SWT grant us a goodness and may He grant us wealth that will be a means of our entry into paradise and not wealth that will be a means of our destruction.

00:06:16.090 --> 00:06:25.090
So that was very interesting that even though it was his own brother, but he felt towards him to say the truth and to say look you better get a maximum amount from this man.

00:06:25.090 --> 00:06:28.090
May Allah SWT grant us goodness.

00:06:29.090 --> 00:06:42.090
And the last point we'd like to mention is, as we said yesterday, that some of the people who didn't have any wealth to pay or to pay the fine for taking part in the war, some of them didn't have the amount.

00:06:42.090 --> 00:06:51.090
So the Prophet SAW instructed by Allah SWT, he let some of them go without even taking any amount from them.

00:06:51.090 --> 00:06:56.090
One of them was Abu Azzah Al-Sha'ir and we will come to see his story a little bit later on.

00:06:56.090 --> 00:07:03.090
We said it yesterday, part of it, that when he told the Prophet SAW, look, I am a person who really doesn't have much.

00:07:03.090 --> 00:07:08.090
My family is big and they need me and so on and I really don't have anything to give you.

00:07:08.090 --> 00:07:15.090
He was then sent away and Rasulullah SAW told him, you don't ever engage in what you did in the future.

00:07:15.090 --> 00:07:17.090
And he said, okay, I won't.

00:07:17.090 --> 00:07:25.090
Now, from amongst those who were taken captive were some who didn't have anything but they were educated.

00:07:25.090 --> 00:07:26.090
They could read and write.

00:07:26.090 --> 00:07:29.090
So the Prophet SAW issued an instruction.

00:07:29.090 --> 00:07:37.090
He said, if any one of you can teach 10 of the youngsters of the Ansar how to read and write, we set you free.

00:07:37.090 --> 00:07:38.090
Subhanallah.

00:07:38.090 --> 00:07:47.090
This showed that the value of learning to read and write and education and the value of being able to understand and so on

00:07:47.090 --> 00:07:54.090
was so high that people were granted their freedom just by teaching people how to read and write.

00:07:54.090 --> 00:07:57.090
And I normally raise a point when it comes to the teachers.

00:07:57.090 --> 00:08:01.090
These people who were captive were not Muslim.

00:08:01.090 --> 00:08:03.090
And for them, what was their paradise?

00:08:03.090 --> 00:08:08.090
Their paradise was to be set free so that they could live the rest of their lives according to their own desires.

00:08:08.090 --> 00:08:17.090
So they were told, if you teach 10 people to read and write, you will get your paradise in the sense that you're going to be free in this world.

00:08:17.090 --> 00:08:19.090
And for you, the world is the paradise.

00:08:19.090 --> 00:08:29.090
So those who teach the Muslims how to read and write from amongst the Muslims and those from amongst the Muslims to this day.

00:08:29.090 --> 00:08:34.090
And we know that teaching is now a profession that many people are turning away from.

00:08:34.090 --> 00:08:43.090
Because it is one of the only professions where your progress is gauged by the examination of someone else.

00:08:43.090 --> 00:08:44.090
Have you ever thought of that?

00:08:44.090 --> 00:08:47.090
A teacher is tested by who?

00:08:47.090 --> 00:08:53.090
Not by whether they know it or not, but by whether other people know what they've taught them or not.

00:08:53.090 --> 00:08:56.090
So it's very difficult and nowadays people don't really want to teach.

00:08:56.090 --> 00:09:00.090
Ask those running schools, may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness.

00:09:00.090 --> 00:09:10.090
The point I am raising is imagine how valuable the reward is that Allah is giving these mushriks of Quraish what they wanted.

00:09:10.090 --> 00:09:14.090
Is it impossible for Allah to give us our paradise as a result?

00:09:14.090 --> 00:09:17.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant that to us.

00:09:17.090 --> 00:09:19.090
And may He make us from those who can teach.

00:09:19.090 --> 00:09:22.090
Because definitely even the Prophet salallahu alaihi wa sallam says,

00:09:22.090 --> 00:09:26.090
I was actually sent as a teacher.

00:09:26.090 --> 00:09:32.090
Obviously the teachings he taught were very spiritual and connected to the link with Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala.

00:09:32.090 --> 00:09:39.090
But he was also a teacher and he was a powerful teacher and he did not beat any of his students.

00:09:39.090 --> 00:09:43.090
And at the same time, they learned absolutely everything that he had taught them.

00:09:43.090 --> 00:09:47.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us even a portion of that baraka.

00:09:47.090 --> 00:09:55.090
Now as we said yesterday, we ended on a point that Banu Qaynuqa' they were people who were living within Madinah Munawwara.

00:09:55.090 --> 00:10:01.090
There were three clans of the Jewish people around Madinah 2 and within Madinah 1 of them.

00:10:01.090 --> 00:10:06.090
So Banu Qaynuqa' was inside Madinah and as for Banu Qurayza and Banu al-Nadheer,

00:10:06.090 --> 00:10:09.090
they were on the outskirts of Madinah Munawwara.

00:10:09.090 --> 00:10:12.090
In the marketplace of Banu Qaynuqa' something had happened.

00:10:12.090 --> 00:10:19.090
But prior to that, Banu Qaynuqa' were very, very upset when the Quraysh had suffered a defeat

00:10:19.090 --> 00:10:23.090
and Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam and his companions had come back.

00:10:23.090 --> 00:10:29.090
Allah calls the day of Badr Yawmal Furqan, the day of the criterion,

00:10:29.090 --> 00:10:34.090
the day that the deciding factor or the day of the deciding factor.

00:10:34.090 --> 00:10:38.090
The Muslims had won and it was a huge victory.

00:10:38.090 --> 00:10:40.090
These people were upset. Why?

00:10:40.090 --> 00:10:45.090
Because they were hoping that this Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam and his people would lose

00:10:45.090 --> 00:10:50.090
and then we would be the leaders once again because they could not engage in all their mischief

00:10:50.090 --> 00:10:55.090
when the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam is in their midst or in Madinah Munawwara.

00:10:55.090 --> 00:11:03.090
So they had teamed up with one of the hypocrites who joined Islam only for show.

00:11:03.090 --> 00:11:07.090
How do we know that? How do we know that this man was a hypocrite?

00:11:07.090 --> 00:11:12.090
We can never know unless we were told by Allah and His Rasul sallallahu alayhi wasallam.

00:11:12.090 --> 00:11:18.090
So Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam informed us that Allah informed him a list of names of people

00:11:18.090 --> 00:11:23.090
who were actually not Muslim but they were just pretending because they had had no other option

00:11:23.090 --> 00:11:26.090
or they felt that it was in the best of their interests.

00:11:26.090 --> 00:11:30.090
From amongst them was this man Abdullah ibn Ubay ibn Saloon.

00:11:30.090 --> 00:11:32.090
He had accepted Islam just after that.

00:11:32.090 --> 00:11:36.090
It is made mention of in a lot of the narrations that it was after the Battle of Badr

00:11:36.090 --> 00:11:41.090
and this is when he saw that the Muslims have quite a bit of power and let me join forces with them.

00:11:41.090 --> 00:11:46.090
So he had teamed up with the people of Quraysh and he had teamed up with Banu Qaynuqa'

00:11:46.090 --> 00:11:53.090
and he tried to tamper with Banu al-Nadir and the others and Allah sallallahu alayhi wasallam exposed him every single time.

00:11:53.090 --> 00:12:00.090
So in the marketplace of Banu Qaynuqa' was a Muslim Sahabiyya who was seated

00:12:00.090 --> 00:12:05.090
and she was seated, her name is not given to us and obviously if you look at the books of Islamic history

00:12:05.090 --> 00:12:10.090
you find whenever something bad has happened to someone the name is always protected in a lot of cases

00:12:10.090 --> 00:12:17.090
so that people wouldn't actually be able to say oh this person and that person may Allah sallallahu alayhi wasallam grant us protection

00:12:17.090 --> 00:12:20.090
and even though it's not relevant for us to know certain things.

00:12:20.090 --> 00:12:25.090
We need to know there was one of our sisters, one of the Sahabiyat, may Allah be pleased with her.

00:12:25.090 --> 00:12:31.090
As she was sitting down the bottom of her dress was tied to the top of it with a little stitch

00:12:31.090 --> 00:12:35.090
by one of these mischievous men of Banu Qaynuqa'

00:12:35.090 --> 00:12:40.090
and when you were sitting you wouldn't really notice anything because the dress is all around

00:12:40.090 --> 00:12:45.090
and as she got up part of her leg showed so they started laughing at her.

00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:52.090
When they laughed at her one of the Muslims who understood what had happened went to beat up this man from Banu Qaynuqa'

00:12:52.090 --> 00:12:57.090
so much so that he died, the man from Banu Qaynuqa' had died

00:12:57.090 --> 00:13:03.090
and when this happened the people of Banu Qaynuqa' got up and they started beating up this man until he also died

00:13:03.090 --> 00:13:07.090
and thereafter news went to Al-Madeen Al-Munawwara.

00:13:07.090 --> 00:13:11.090
Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam announced war, straight.

00:13:11.090 --> 00:13:15.090
He told his men let's get up and he with Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib radiallahu anhu

00:13:15.090 --> 00:13:18.090
we are going to Banu Qaynuqa' and we will deal with them.

00:13:18.090 --> 00:13:22.090
How dare they break the treaty and they've been engaging in mischief all along

00:13:22.090 --> 00:13:24.090
and now they have killed one of our men

00:13:24.090 --> 00:13:30.090
and they have disrespected or they have made a fool of one of our sisters.

00:13:30.090 --> 00:13:32.090
Subhanallah, how can they do this?

00:13:32.090 --> 00:13:35.090
And so Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam went to them.

00:13:35.090 --> 00:13:42.090
Banu Qaynuqa' was shocked because they had known that this mischief of ours is going to come to the fore at some stage.

00:13:42.090 --> 00:13:45.090
The Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam surrounded them

00:13:45.090 --> 00:13:49.090
and decision was being made as to what to do with these people.

00:13:49.090 --> 00:13:51.090
He surrounded them for 15 days.

00:13:51.090 --> 00:13:53.090
They wanted to fight, they couldn't fight

00:13:53.090 --> 00:13:55.090
because the Muslims had outnumbered them

00:13:55.090 --> 00:14:01.090
and at the same time they succumbed after 15 days to the pressure

00:14:01.090 --> 00:14:04.090
because nothing going in, nothing coming out

00:14:04.090 --> 00:14:09.090
and these people are now surrounded for 15 days and they decided let's talk.

00:14:09.090 --> 00:14:11.090
So decisions were being made.

00:14:11.090 --> 00:14:15.090
The hypocrite Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salool comes to Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:14:15.090 --> 00:14:17.090
and what was his power?

00:14:18.090 --> 00:14:25.090
He claims or he says because I was supposed to be selected the leader of Medina before you came

00:14:25.090 --> 00:14:27.090
so I am one of the top leaders.

00:14:27.090 --> 00:14:31.090
So he placed himself as one of the top leaders.

00:14:31.090 --> 00:14:32.090
Although he was a nobody.

00:14:32.090 --> 00:14:35.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us.

00:14:35.090 --> 00:14:39.090
So this Ubayy comes to Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:14:39.090 --> 00:14:42.090
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salool and he gets hold of him.

00:14:42.090 --> 00:14:44.090
He says release these people

00:14:44.090 --> 00:14:47.090
and Rasoolullah sallallahu alayhi wasallam says leave me alone.

00:14:47.090 --> 00:14:50.090
Meaning you don't need to hold someone in this particular way.

00:14:50.090 --> 00:14:52.090
There is a way of speaking.

00:14:52.090 --> 00:14:55.090
He says no I won't leave you until you leave these people

00:14:55.090 --> 00:15:00.090
because when I had before you came difficulty with other tribes they protected us

00:15:00.090 --> 00:15:02.090
and these were the people who did this and who did that

00:15:02.090 --> 00:15:04.090
and they had safeguarded us with their lives

00:15:04.090 --> 00:15:09.090
and today just because they did one thing you want to now execute them and so on.

00:15:09.090 --> 00:15:13.090
So the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam said okay he was quite upset

00:15:13.090 --> 00:15:17.090
and he said okay we will leave them but they must leave Madinah Munawwara.

00:15:17.090 --> 00:15:18.090
They must go.

00:15:18.090 --> 00:15:21.090
This little sabbath must be clear, empty.

00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:25.090
So now that was a decision made by the instruction of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:15:25.090 --> 00:15:31.090
Banu Qaynuqaa a little sabbath in Madinah Munawwara where these people were based.

00:15:31.090 --> 00:15:33.090
They were told we are giving you three days.

00:15:33.090 --> 00:15:35.090
You take your children, your families and you walk out.

00:15:35.090 --> 00:15:37.090
Everything else you leave here.

00:15:37.090 --> 00:15:38.090
You go.

00:15:38.090 --> 00:15:41.090
And the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam who had gone with Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib

00:15:41.090 --> 00:15:43.090
with a group of men.

00:15:43.090 --> 00:15:49.090
The Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam had placed Ubadah ibn As-Samit radiallahu anhu

00:15:49.090 --> 00:15:54.090
as a person who would oversee and supervise the fact that these people left.

00:15:54.090 --> 00:15:56.090
And within three days they were gone.

00:15:56.090 --> 00:15:57.090
Where did they go?

00:15:57.090 --> 00:15:59.090
They all left to Adhru'at.

00:15:59.090 --> 00:16:03.090
And they were actually very fortunate that the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:16:03.090 --> 00:16:08.090
did not execute some of those perpetrators because by right they had murdered someone

00:16:08.090 --> 00:16:10.090
and they had engaged in mischief.

00:16:10.090 --> 00:16:16.090
So there could have been a court case there which would be decided within moments

00:16:16.090 --> 00:16:18.090
and a few of them would have been executed.

00:16:18.090 --> 00:16:21.090
But he did them a favor by telling them okay just leave.

00:16:21.090 --> 00:16:24.090
More or less exiling them, sending them away.

00:16:24.090 --> 00:16:28.090
So they had gone to a place known as Adhru'at close to Al-Sham which is

00:16:28.090 --> 00:16:30.090
as we always say the Syrian region.

00:16:30.090 --> 00:16:34.090
The reason why I say region, some people think that Al-Sham refers to Syria.

00:16:34.090 --> 00:16:41.090
No, it refers to Syria, Lebanon as well as Palestine and northern Saudi Arabia as well.

00:16:41.090 --> 00:16:44.090
That entire part is referred to as Al-Sham.

00:16:44.090 --> 00:16:47.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us a deep understanding.

00:16:47.090 --> 00:16:53.090
So this was what had happened for the people or to the people of Banu Qaynuqa'

00:16:53.090 --> 00:16:55.090
a lesson for us all.

00:16:55.090 --> 00:17:00.090
The respect and dignity of a Muslim, male or female, should be at our hearts.

00:17:00.090 --> 00:17:03.090
We should feel pain when one of us is harmed or hurt.

00:17:03.090 --> 00:17:06.090
And this is the teaching of Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam.

00:17:06.090 --> 00:17:09.090
He says al-mu'minuna, the believers are like one body.

00:17:09.090 --> 00:17:13.090
The head is hurt, the rest of the body is restless.

00:17:13.090 --> 00:17:16.090
A little finger is hurt, the whole body is restless.

00:17:16.090 --> 00:17:20.090
The day we feel that way we will resolve the matters of the Ummah.

00:17:20.090 --> 00:17:24.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala return us to those genuine feelings today.

00:17:24.090 --> 00:17:29.090
Amongst us in one community we have hatred ten ways.

00:17:29.090 --> 00:17:32.090
This group and that group and this one don't talk to that one

00:17:32.090 --> 00:17:34.090
and that one his own brother he doesn't speak to.

00:17:34.090 --> 00:17:37.090
And the other one when he hears that this person has had damage

00:17:37.090 --> 00:17:40.090
he is excited and says alhamdulillah instead of saying

00:17:40.090 --> 00:17:42.090
may Allah safeguard us and grant him goodness.

00:17:42.090 --> 00:17:44.090
We become happy at the loss of others.

00:17:44.090 --> 00:17:49.090
لا تظهر الشماتة لأخيك فيرحمه الله ويبتليك

00:17:49.090 --> 00:17:51.090
Do not become happy at the loss of your brother

00:17:51.090 --> 00:17:54.090
because Allah may have mercy on him

00:17:54.090 --> 00:17:57.090
and test you with something similar if not worse.

00:17:57.090 --> 00:18:00.090
May Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness.

00:18:00.090 --> 00:18:04.090
Thereafter in the same year it is reported or in the following year

00:18:04.090 --> 00:18:07.090
it is reported now we are talking of the third year of Hijra

00:18:07.090 --> 00:18:09.090
that the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam

00:18:09.090 --> 00:18:11.090
got his daughter Fatima radiallahu anha

00:18:11.090 --> 00:18:15.090
married to Ali ibn Abi Talib radiallahu anhu very briefly.

00:18:15.090 --> 00:18:17.090
I can make mention of what happened.

00:18:17.090 --> 00:18:19.090
One of the servants of Ali radiallahu anhu

00:18:19.090 --> 00:18:21.090
had come up to him and said did you hear

00:18:21.090 --> 00:18:24.090
that the daughter of the Prophet salallahu alaihi wasallam Fatima

00:18:24.090 --> 00:18:26.090
is now of marriage age.

00:18:26.090 --> 00:18:28.090
And at that time they used to marry very early

00:18:28.090 --> 00:18:31.090
12 years old, 13, 14, 15 years old

00:18:31.090 --> 00:18:33.090
and by that time they were all married

00:18:33.090 --> 00:18:35.090
and sometimes even earlier than that

00:18:35.090 --> 00:18:38.090
you have cases of people who married a little bit earlier

00:18:38.090 --> 00:18:41.090
at the ages of 6 and 7 and 8

00:18:41.090 --> 00:18:44.090
and they did not get together or they did not live together

00:18:44.090 --> 00:18:46.090
until they arrived at puberty.

00:18:46.090 --> 00:18:51.090
When they arrived at puberty at the age of 10 or 11 or 12 and so on

00:18:51.090 --> 00:18:54.090
they then were sent to live with their husbands

00:18:54.090 --> 00:18:56.090
and Alhamdulillah this was the norm of the time

00:18:56.090 --> 00:18:59.090
and as you know the norms change with the changing of times

00:18:59.090 --> 00:19:02.090
so what is normal today might seem different

00:19:02.090 --> 00:19:04.090
from what was normal at that time

00:19:04.090 --> 00:19:05.090
but it was the norm

00:19:05.090 --> 00:19:07.090
and what is the norm in one area

00:19:07.090 --> 00:19:09.090
sometimes is different in another area

00:19:09.090 --> 00:19:11.090
so we should not get excited

00:19:11.090 --> 00:19:13.090
and we should not start picking on people

00:19:13.090 --> 00:19:14.090
it was their norm

00:19:14.090 --> 00:19:16.090
if there was anything wrong in anything that was happening

00:19:16.090 --> 00:19:18.090
the people there would have stopped it

00:19:18.090 --> 00:19:20.090
but Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala's mercy

00:19:20.090 --> 00:19:23.090
and Allah has granted some form of level of acceptance

00:19:23.090 --> 00:19:26.090
or to the norm of the people that is acceptable

00:19:26.090 --> 00:19:28.090
and this was part of it.

00:19:28.090 --> 00:19:30.090
Yesterday we made mention of

00:19:30.090 --> 00:19:33.090
the other two daughters of Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:19:33.090 --> 00:19:35.090
Ruqayya and Umm Kulthum

00:19:35.090 --> 00:19:38.090
and I had said that they were married to the sons of Abu Lahab.

00:19:38.090 --> 00:19:41.090
If you open the books of Islamic history

00:19:41.090 --> 00:19:45.090
yes there is report of them having been married to the sons of Abu Lahab

00:19:45.090 --> 00:19:48.090
and when Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam came to spread Islam

00:19:48.090 --> 00:19:51.090
then he instructed his sons to divorce them

00:19:51.090 --> 00:19:53.090
and to leave them because he said

00:19:53.090 --> 00:19:55.090
I don't want you to be with these

00:19:55.090 --> 00:19:58.090
who are the children of this man

00:19:58.090 --> 00:20:00.090
who is inflicting so much harm

00:20:00.090 --> 00:20:04.090
or who has reneged from the religion of his forefathers.

00:20:04.090 --> 00:20:06.090
Now there are two narrations.

00:20:06.090 --> 00:20:08.090
One says that they were married

00:20:08.090 --> 00:20:10.090
but they had not consummated

00:20:10.090 --> 00:20:12.090
in the sense that it was fixed

00:20:12.090 --> 00:20:14.090
like Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:20:14.090 --> 00:20:16.090
being married to Aisha radiallahu anha

00:20:16.090 --> 00:20:18.090
but there was no consummation at all

00:20:18.090 --> 00:20:19.090
it happened later on

00:20:19.090 --> 00:20:20.090
so in the same way this

00:20:20.090 --> 00:20:21.090
there was no consummation

00:20:21.090 --> 00:20:23.090
more or less what we would term today

00:20:23.090 --> 00:20:25.090
these people are engaged

00:20:25.090 --> 00:20:27.090
and they will get together at some stage

00:20:27.090 --> 00:20:29.090
before they got together already

00:20:29.090 --> 00:20:30.090
these two were released

00:20:30.090 --> 00:20:31.090
and later on they were married to

00:20:31.090 --> 00:20:33.090
Uthman ibn Affan radiallahu anha

00:20:33.090 --> 00:20:36.090
first Ruqayya binti Rasulillahi sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:20:36.090 --> 00:20:38.090
and just after the battle of Badr

00:20:38.090 --> 00:20:39.090
she passed away

00:20:39.090 --> 00:20:43.090
imagine the difficulty of the messenger sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:20:43.090 --> 00:20:45.090
he had to go through a lot

00:20:45.090 --> 00:20:46.090
he lost his sons

00:20:46.090 --> 00:20:47.090
he lost his sons

00:20:47.090 --> 00:20:50.090
now he is losing his own daughter

00:20:50.090 --> 00:20:52.090
and he lost his daughters

00:20:52.090 --> 00:20:53.090
all of them besides one

00:20:53.090 --> 00:20:55.090
before he passed away himself

00:20:55.090 --> 00:20:56.090
and he lost them

00:20:56.090 --> 00:20:57.090
subhanallah

00:20:57.090 --> 00:21:00.090
and yet he used to pray to Allah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:21:00.090 --> 00:21:02.090
this is why when we lose our children before us

00:21:02.090 --> 00:21:05.090
we should always pray to Allah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:21:05.090 --> 00:21:08.090
Ya Allah make this a means of my entry into paradise

00:21:08.090 --> 00:21:10.090
if the messenger went through this difficulty

00:21:10.090 --> 00:21:13.090
that means you have chosen me to go through the same difficulty

00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:15.090
that the messenger has gone through

00:21:15.090 --> 00:21:17.090
and perhaps Ya Allah grant me a good reward

00:21:17.090 --> 00:21:19.090
may Allah sallallahu alaihi wasallam open our doors

00:21:19.090 --> 00:21:21.090
and have mercy on all of us

00:21:21.090 --> 00:21:23.090
and on those who have lost their children

00:21:23.090 --> 00:21:25.090
before their own death

00:21:25.090 --> 00:21:28.090
may Allah sallallahu alaihi wasallam grant us ease

00:21:28.090 --> 00:21:32.090
so when Ali radiallahu anhu heard this

00:21:32.090 --> 00:21:35.340
in fact I was making mention of the other narration

00:21:35.340 --> 00:21:38.340
the other narration says that they were married

00:21:38.340 --> 00:21:39.340
and thereafter divorced

00:21:39.340 --> 00:21:44.340
however we would like to give perhaps strength to the narration

00:21:44.340 --> 00:21:46.340
that says it was not consummated yet

00:21:46.340 --> 00:21:48.340
and they had divorced them

00:21:48.340 --> 00:21:51.340
with Ali radiallahu anhu when he heard this

00:21:51.340 --> 00:21:54.340
he wanted to speak to Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:21:54.340 --> 00:21:56.340
but he was a bit shy

00:21:56.340 --> 00:21:58.340
and he was told no if you go

00:21:58.340 --> 00:22:01.340
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam will agree

00:22:01.340 --> 00:22:03.340
so he comes to Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:22:03.340 --> 00:22:05.340
and he sits in front of him

00:22:05.340 --> 00:22:08.340
and he says Ya Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:22:08.340 --> 00:22:09.340
then he is quiet

00:22:09.340 --> 00:22:11.340
so the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam says

00:22:11.340 --> 00:22:12.340
is there something you want to say

00:22:12.340 --> 00:22:13.340
oh Ali

00:22:13.340 --> 00:22:14.340
he keeps quiet

00:22:14.340 --> 00:22:15.340
oh it's okay

00:22:15.340 --> 00:22:16.340
he says

00:22:16.340 --> 00:22:19.340
do you want to talk to me about my daughter Fatima

00:22:19.340 --> 00:22:20.340
Subhanallah

00:22:20.340 --> 00:22:22.340
Allah sallallahu alaihi wasallam grant us an understanding

00:22:22.340 --> 00:22:23.340
look at this

00:22:23.340 --> 00:22:26.340
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam already instructed

00:22:26.340 --> 00:22:27.340
what is happening

00:22:27.340 --> 00:22:29.340
do you want to talk to me about my daughter Fatima

00:22:29.340 --> 00:22:30.340
he says yes

00:22:30.340 --> 00:22:32.340
he says what do you have

00:22:32.340 --> 00:22:34.340
in the sense that

00:22:34.340 --> 00:22:36.340
are you going to pay her the mahr

00:22:36.340 --> 00:22:37.340
now this in Islam

00:22:37.340 --> 00:22:39.340
mahr is not actually a dowry

00:22:39.340 --> 00:22:41.340
because a dowry

00:22:41.340 --> 00:22:43.340
what happens in some of the cases

00:22:43.340 --> 00:22:45.340
they pay an amount to the father

00:22:45.340 --> 00:22:46.340
to the mother

00:22:46.340 --> 00:22:47.340
to the grandfather

00:22:47.340 --> 00:22:48.340
to the uncles

00:22:48.340 --> 00:22:49.340
to the aunts

00:22:49.340 --> 00:22:51.340
and they have to pay over so many years

00:22:51.340 --> 00:22:52.340
and who eats the money

00:22:52.340 --> 00:22:54.340
the parents and the others

00:22:54.340 --> 00:22:56.340
in Islam there is nothing like that

00:22:56.340 --> 00:22:58.340
we say we do not sell human beings

00:22:58.340 --> 00:23:00.340
the amount at marriage

00:23:00.340 --> 00:23:02.340
is from the groom to the bride

00:23:02.340 --> 00:23:03.340
that's it

00:23:03.340 --> 00:23:06.340
no other amounts are compulsory in Islam

00:23:06.340 --> 00:23:09.340
if there is anything you want to give out of your goodness

00:23:09.340 --> 00:23:11.340
to your father in law or to anyone else

00:23:11.340 --> 00:23:12.340
no problem

00:23:12.340 --> 00:23:14.340
but it is not an Islamic requirement

00:23:14.340 --> 00:23:16.340
the mahr in Islam means

00:23:16.340 --> 00:23:18.340
an amount from the groom

00:23:18.340 --> 00:23:19.340
to the bride

00:23:19.340 --> 00:23:21.340
it is basically a payment to say from today on

00:23:21.340 --> 00:23:23.340
your responsibility is mine

00:23:23.340 --> 00:23:25.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us

00:23:25.340 --> 00:23:26.340
an understanding

00:23:26.340 --> 00:23:28.340
so when people say dowry

00:23:28.340 --> 00:23:29.340
it must not be misunderstood

00:23:29.340 --> 00:23:31.340
in Islam there is nothing like a dowry

00:23:31.340 --> 00:23:33.340
that we see across the globe

00:23:33.340 --> 00:23:35.340
it is simply an amount from here to there

00:23:35.340 --> 00:23:37.340
from the groom to the bride

00:23:37.340 --> 00:23:40.340
as for those who brought up these girls

00:23:40.340 --> 00:23:41.340
the parents of the girls

00:23:41.340 --> 00:23:42.340
the hadith says

00:23:42.340 --> 00:23:44.340
the prophet peace be upon him says

00:23:44.340 --> 00:23:45.340
for you is paradise

00:23:45.340 --> 00:23:47.340
you have brought up someone

00:23:47.340 --> 00:23:49.340
to go and live in someone else's home

00:23:49.340 --> 00:23:51.340
what you get in return is jannah

00:23:51.340 --> 00:23:52.340
it is paradise

00:23:52.340 --> 00:23:53.340
and this is why the hadith says

00:23:53.340 --> 00:23:54.340
whoever has two daughters

00:23:54.340 --> 00:23:56.340
one narration says three daughters

00:23:56.340 --> 00:23:57.340
and looks after them well

00:23:57.340 --> 00:23:58.340
brings them up

00:23:58.340 --> 00:23:59.340
amanah as a trust

00:23:59.340 --> 00:24:01.340
gets them married to good homes

00:24:01.340 --> 00:24:03.340
that will result in their upliftment

00:24:03.340 --> 00:24:04.340
spiritually and so on

00:24:04.340 --> 00:24:06.340
for them will be paradise

00:24:06.340 --> 00:24:08.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness

00:24:08.340 --> 00:24:09.340
so he said

00:24:09.340 --> 00:24:11.340
look I don't have anything at all

00:24:11.340 --> 00:24:12.340
so the prophet says

00:24:12.340 --> 00:24:13.340
peace be upon him

00:24:13.340 --> 00:24:14.340
what about the shield

00:24:14.340 --> 00:24:16.340
I gave you once

00:24:16.340 --> 00:24:17.340
he says I've got that

00:24:17.340 --> 00:24:20.340
he says well we can get that sold

00:24:20.340 --> 00:24:22.340
and you will get a certain amount for it

00:24:22.340 --> 00:24:24.340
and you can pay that as a mahr

00:24:24.340 --> 00:24:26.340
and this is how the prophet

00:24:26.340 --> 00:24:27.340
peace be upon him

00:24:27.340 --> 00:24:29.340
got his daughter married

00:24:29.340 --> 00:24:31.340
to Ali ibn Abi Talib r.a

00:24:31.340 --> 00:24:33.340
when he was a man

00:24:33.340 --> 00:24:35.340
whose financial standing was zero

00:24:35.340 --> 00:24:36.340
he had nothing

00:24:36.340 --> 00:24:37.340
absolutely no

00:24:37.340 --> 00:24:39.340
today when our daughters want to marry someone

00:24:39.340 --> 00:24:40.340
we first look at

00:24:40.340 --> 00:24:42.340
how much money does he have

00:24:42.340 --> 00:24:43.340
you know what

00:24:43.340 --> 00:24:44.340
they might suffer

00:24:44.340 --> 00:24:45.340
he's too poor

00:24:45.340 --> 00:24:46.340
how do you know

00:24:46.340 --> 00:24:47.340
after they get married

00:24:47.340 --> 00:24:48.340
he might lose everything

00:24:48.340 --> 00:24:49.340
then what happens

00:24:49.340 --> 00:24:50.340
and do you know

00:24:50.340 --> 00:24:51.340
if you look at our parents

00:24:51.340 --> 00:24:53.340
and I'm sure a lot of those

00:24:53.340 --> 00:24:55.340
who are of a middle age here

00:24:55.340 --> 00:24:59.340
started off very very humbly

00:24:59.340 --> 00:25:01.340
and slowly worked up the ladder

00:25:01.340 --> 00:25:04.340
now when they are 50, 60 years old

00:25:04.340 --> 00:25:05.340
they can afford everything

00:25:05.340 --> 00:25:06.340
but now for themselves

00:25:06.340 --> 00:25:07.340
their own children

00:25:07.340 --> 00:25:09.340
they're saying look for a rich man

00:25:09.340 --> 00:25:10.340
but think about how you started

00:25:10.340 --> 00:25:11.340
my beloved brother

00:25:11.340 --> 00:25:12.340
my beloved sister

00:25:12.340 --> 00:25:14.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:25:14.340 --> 00:25:15.340
grant us the ability

00:25:15.340 --> 00:25:16.340
to look at the deen

00:25:16.340 --> 00:25:18.340
look at Ali ibn Abi Talib

00:25:18.340 --> 00:25:19.340
he was a cousin

00:25:19.340 --> 00:25:23.340
a friend of Rasulullah s.a.w. as well

00:25:23.340 --> 00:25:26.340
and they had had days together

00:25:26.340 --> 00:25:28.340
in Makkah al-Mukarramah

00:25:28.340 --> 00:25:30.340
and he was the first from the youngsters

00:25:30.340 --> 00:25:32.340
who had accepted Islam

00:25:32.340 --> 00:25:33.340
and here the prophet

00:25:33.340 --> 00:25:36.340
s.a.w. is giving him his daughter

00:25:36.340 --> 00:25:37.340
and the prophet s.a.w. says

00:25:37.340 --> 00:25:39.340
where's the shield I gave you

00:25:39.340 --> 00:25:41.340
which means it was actually from me

00:25:41.340 --> 00:25:42.340
to be honest with you anyway

00:25:42.340 --> 00:25:44.340
now you're getting it back

00:25:44.340 --> 00:25:45.340
it's reported that

00:25:45.340 --> 00:25:50.340
they sold it for 400 Daraahim

00:25:50.340 --> 00:25:52.340
and they had given that

00:25:52.340 --> 00:25:55.340
or he had given that as a mahr

00:25:55.340 --> 00:25:59.340
to Fatima radiallahu anha

00:25:59.340 --> 00:26:00.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:00.340 --> 00:26:02.340
grant us acceptance

00:26:02.340 --> 00:26:03.340
and may he make us from those

00:26:03.340 --> 00:26:05.340
who realize and understand

00:26:05.340 --> 00:26:08.340
from the lessons that we've derived from this

00:26:08.340 --> 00:26:11.340
then also Uthman ibn Affan radiallahu anhu

00:26:11.340 --> 00:26:13.340
as we've heard

00:26:13.340 --> 00:26:15.340
the one wife of his Ruqayya

00:26:15.340 --> 00:26:18.340
the daughter of Rasulullah s.a.w. passed away

00:26:18.340 --> 00:26:19.340
after some time

00:26:19.340 --> 00:26:21.340
it's reported that after some time

00:26:21.340 --> 00:26:23.340
the prophet s.a.w. got him married

00:26:23.340 --> 00:26:26.340
to his other daughter Um Kulthum

00:26:26.340 --> 00:26:28.340
and this is why Uthman was known as the Nurayn

00:26:28.340 --> 00:26:30.340
we made mention of this yesterday

00:26:30.340 --> 00:26:31.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:26:31.340 --> 00:26:33.340
grant us happy homes

00:26:33.340 --> 00:26:34.340
may he grant us spouses

00:26:34.340 --> 00:26:37.340
who will be the coolness of our eyes, Ameen

00:26:37.340 --> 00:26:39.340
we have another thing that happened

00:26:39.340 --> 00:26:41.340
after the battle of Badr

00:26:41.340 --> 00:26:43.340
and after Banu Qaynuqa and so on

00:26:43.340 --> 00:26:45.340
there were certain people who were criminals

00:26:45.340 --> 00:26:48.340
who were sought after by the Muslims

00:26:48.340 --> 00:26:50.340
by the prophet s.a.w.

00:26:50.340 --> 00:26:51.340
because of their crimes

00:26:51.340 --> 00:26:54.340
crimes against humanity, against the Muslims

00:26:54.340 --> 00:26:55.340
because of what they had done

00:26:55.340 --> 00:26:58.340
and these were criminals of the highest order

00:26:58.340 --> 00:27:00.340
the prophet s.a.w.

00:27:00.340 --> 00:27:02.340
ordered their execution

00:27:02.340 --> 00:27:04.340
and a few of them were executed from amongst them

00:27:04.340 --> 00:27:07.340
was one leader from amongst the Jews

00:27:07.340 --> 00:27:09.340
who was known as Ka'b ibn al-Ashraf

00:27:09.340 --> 00:27:13.340
and he was very very venomous, very dangerous

00:27:13.340 --> 00:27:15.340
he has caused lots of harm to the Muslims

00:27:15.340 --> 00:27:19.340
and he was a person who was really a criminal of note

00:27:19.340 --> 00:27:22.340
and the prophet s.a.w. instructed his execution

00:27:22.340 --> 00:27:24.340
and he was executed

00:27:24.340 --> 00:27:26.340
and this came as a lesson for all those

00:27:26.340 --> 00:27:27.340
who intended harm

00:27:27.340 --> 00:27:29.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala protect us

00:27:29.340 --> 00:27:32.340
now we move on to the next battle

00:27:32.340 --> 00:27:34.340
the next major battle that took place

00:27:34.340 --> 00:27:35.340
was the battle of Uhud

00:27:35.340 --> 00:27:38.340
between Badr and Uhud there were skirmishes

00:27:38.340 --> 00:27:39.340
there were a few little battles

00:27:39.340 --> 00:27:42.340
a few little run-ins between the Muslims

00:27:42.340 --> 00:27:43.340
and some of the Mushriks

00:27:43.340 --> 00:27:45.340
some of those who had taken part

00:27:45.340 --> 00:27:47.340
on the side of Quraish

00:27:47.340 --> 00:27:49.340
when it came to the battle of Badr

00:27:49.340 --> 00:27:50.340
and they were just being dealt with

00:27:50.340 --> 00:27:52.340
and sorted out, nothing major

00:27:52.340 --> 00:27:54.340
but the kuffar of Quraish

00:27:54.340 --> 00:27:56.340
when they got back to Makkah

00:27:56.340 --> 00:27:57.340
they heard the news

00:27:57.340 --> 00:27:58.340
they were upset

00:27:58.340 --> 00:28:01.340
Quraish had banned crying

00:28:01.340 --> 00:28:02.340
nobody is allowed to cry

00:28:02.340 --> 00:28:03.340
why? if we cry

00:28:03.340 --> 00:28:05.340
the Muslims are going to laugh at us

00:28:05.340 --> 00:28:07.340
so no one is allowed to cry over their dead

00:28:07.340 --> 00:28:11.340
although the leaders were executed in that war

00:28:11.340 --> 00:28:13.340
so what did Quraish do?

00:28:13.340 --> 00:28:16.340
they got together at Dar al-Najwa

00:28:16.340 --> 00:28:17.340
that house

00:28:17.340 --> 00:28:20.340
and subhanallah

00:28:20.340 --> 00:28:22.340
they decided with Abu Sufyan

00:28:22.340 --> 00:28:25.340
that you know now you are one of our leaders here

00:28:25.340 --> 00:28:27.340
you are the man who came with the caravan

00:28:27.340 --> 00:28:28.340
that caravan was saved

00:28:28.340 --> 00:28:30.340
so every one of us

00:28:30.340 --> 00:28:32.340
all the prophets we've made from that caravan

00:28:32.340 --> 00:28:34.340
we are going to use that

00:28:34.340 --> 00:28:36.340
contributing it to another war

00:28:36.340 --> 00:28:39.340
that we are going to take to the Muslims in Madinah

00:28:39.340 --> 00:28:41.340
and crush them once and for all

00:28:41.340 --> 00:28:43.340
how much money did they make from there?

00:28:43.340 --> 00:28:46.340
fifty thousand dinars

00:28:46.340 --> 00:28:47.340
dinars are gold coins

00:28:47.340 --> 00:28:50.340
they had made fifty thousand gold coins

00:28:50.340 --> 00:28:53.340
you know I was just reading this today

00:28:53.340 --> 00:28:55.340
and thinking to myself

00:28:55.340 --> 00:28:57.340
a group of camels

00:28:57.340 --> 00:28:59.340
at that time

00:28:59.340 --> 00:29:01.340
coming from Ash-Sham

00:29:01.340 --> 00:29:02.340
right down to Makkah

00:29:02.340 --> 00:29:04.340
and in one container

00:29:04.340 --> 00:29:08.340
they made fifty thousand gold coins

00:29:08.340 --> 00:29:09.340
subhanallah

00:29:09.340 --> 00:29:11.340
what type of business people were these?

00:29:11.340 --> 00:29:13.340
today mashallah we can bring two three containers

00:29:13.340 --> 00:29:15.340
do you think you would get profit of

00:29:15.340 --> 00:29:18.340
fifty thousand gold coins just by that?

00:29:18.340 --> 00:29:21.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us baraka

00:29:21.340 --> 00:29:22.340
in whatever He gives us

00:29:22.340 --> 00:29:24.340
so this was the business mind

00:29:24.340 --> 00:29:25.340
of the people of Quraysh

00:29:25.340 --> 00:29:26.340
they were shrewd

00:29:26.340 --> 00:29:27.340
and they knew how to make money

00:29:27.340 --> 00:29:29.340
and now they all promised

00:29:29.340 --> 00:29:30.340
at that house Dar al-Nadwa

00:29:30.340 --> 00:29:31.340
they said

00:29:31.340 --> 00:29:32.340
Abu Sufyan

00:29:32.340 --> 00:29:33.340
you are our leader

00:29:33.340 --> 00:29:34.340
all this wealth

00:29:34.340 --> 00:29:35.340
we all coming out

00:29:35.340 --> 00:29:36.340
everyone is going to come out

00:29:36.340 --> 00:29:38.340
and so with this fifty thousand

00:29:38.340 --> 00:29:39.340
they had bought

00:29:39.340 --> 00:29:40.340
or they had purchased

00:29:40.340 --> 00:29:41.340
lots of weaponry

00:29:41.340 --> 00:29:42.340
and sorted it out

00:29:42.340 --> 00:29:43.340
made it very

00:29:43.340 --> 00:29:44.340
you know

00:29:44.340 --> 00:29:46.340
sharp and so on

00:29:46.340 --> 00:29:47.340
their spears and arrows

00:29:47.340 --> 00:29:49.340
and they had prepared with their

00:29:49.340 --> 00:29:51.340
armor and shields and what have you

00:29:51.340 --> 00:29:52.340
and the horses

00:29:52.340 --> 00:29:54.340
and the fodder for the horses and so on

00:29:54.340 --> 00:29:55.340
and they were ready

00:29:55.340 --> 00:29:57.340
and they started marching out

00:29:57.340 --> 00:29:59.340
to Madinatul Munawwarah

00:29:59.340 --> 00:30:00.340
once they were ready

00:30:00.340 --> 00:30:01.340
they began to march

00:30:01.340 --> 00:30:03.340
now there were certain people

00:30:03.340 --> 00:30:05.340
who did not go out with them

00:30:05.340 --> 00:30:07.340
who didn't go out with these people?

00:30:07.340 --> 00:30:08.340
from amongst them

00:30:08.340 --> 00:30:09.340
was this man

00:30:09.340 --> 00:30:10.340
Abu Azzah al-Sha'ir

00:30:10.340 --> 00:30:11.340
he said

00:30:11.340 --> 00:30:12.340
look I can't come out

00:30:12.340 --> 00:30:13.340
because I was amongst the captives

00:30:13.340 --> 00:30:14.340
poor man

00:30:14.340 --> 00:30:16.340
when Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:16.340 --> 00:30:17.340
released me

00:30:17.340 --> 00:30:18.340
he told me

00:30:18.340 --> 00:30:19.340
don't ever do this again

00:30:19.340 --> 00:30:20.340
and I promised him I wouldn't

00:30:20.340 --> 00:30:21.340
so I'm not going to go back there

00:30:21.340 --> 00:30:22.340
now if they catch me

00:30:22.340 --> 00:30:23.340
I won't be able to

00:30:23.340 --> 00:30:24.340
one narration says

00:30:24.340 --> 00:30:25.340
they put a lot of pressure on him

00:30:25.340 --> 00:30:26.340
and they dragged him with

00:30:26.340 --> 00:30:27.340
another narration says

00:30:27.340 --> 00:30:28.340
no they did not drag him with

00:30:28.340 --> 00:30:29.340
however

00:30:29.340 --> 00:30:31.340
Al-Abbas ibn Abdul Muttalib

00:30:31.340 --> 00:30:34.340
the uncle of Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:34.340 --> 00:30:36.340
who had returned to Makkah

00:30:36.340 --> 00:30:37.340
he also did not come out

00:30:37.340 --> 00:30:38.340
he said I am not coming

00:30:38.340 --> 00:30:39.340
I

00:30:39.340 --> 00:30:41.340
it's very fresh in my mind

00:30:41.340 --> 00:30:42.340
what happened in Badr

00:30:42.340 --> 00:30:43.340
and I'm not interested in fighting

00:30:43.340 --> 00:30:44.340
the Muslims and so on

00:30:44.340 --> 00:30:46.340
and he

00:30:46.340 --> 00:30:47.340
wrote a letter

00:30:47.340 --> 00:30:49.340
to Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:30:49.340 --> 00:30:50.340
his nephew

00:30:50.340 --> 00:30:51.340
oh my nephew

00:30:51.340 --> 00:30:53.340
Quraish is coming out

00:30:53.340 --> 00:30:56.340
with so many men

00:30:56.340 --> 00:30:57.340
and Quraish is coming out

00:30:57.340 --> 00:30:59.340
with three thousand strong men

00:30:59.340 --> 00:31:01.340
now this is three times the size

00:31:01.340 --> 00:31:02.340
of what they came out with

00:31:02.340 --> 00:31:03.340
the first time

00:31:03.340 --> 00:31:04.340
and

00:31:04.340 --> 00:31:06.340
they have so much weaponry

00:31:06.340 --> 00:31:07.340
and they have

00:31:07.340 --> 00:31:08.340
with them their women

00:31:08.340 --> 00:31:10.340
they took out their women as well

00:31:10.340 --> 00:31:11.340
because they said

00:31:11.340 --> 00:31:12.340
if we see our women

00:31:12.340 --> 00:31:13.340
it will encourage us to fight

00:31:13.340 --> 00:31:14.340
because we won't want them

00:31:14.340 --> 00:31:16.340
to become from amongst

00:31:16.340 --> 00:31:18.340
the captives of war

00:31:19.340 --> 00:31:20.340
and they took out

00:31:20.340 --> 00:31:21.340
their women

00:31:21.340 --> 00:31:22.340
their drink

00:31:22.340 --> 00:31:23.340
their dances

00:31:23.340 --> 00:31:24.340
and so on

00:31:24.340 --> 00:31:25.340
they were excited once again

00:31:25.340 --> 00:31:26.340
and they started marching

00:31:26.340 --> 00:31:28.340
the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:31:28.340 --> 00:31:29.340
got information of this

00:31:29.340 --> 00:31:30.340
the letter was received

00:31:30.340 --> 00:31:32.340
by Rasulullah sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:31:32.340 --> 00:31:34.340
in the meantime Quraish

00:31:34.340 --> 00:31:37.340
went to a few of the smaller clans

00:31:37.340 --> 00:31:38.340
Banu al-Mustaliq

00:31:38.340 --> 00:31:40.340
and Banu al-Hun

00:31:40.340 --> 00:31:41.340
and a few others

00:31:41.340 --> 00:31:42.340
and told them

00:31:42.340 --> 00:31:43.340
do you know what

00:31:43.340 --> 00:31:44.340
we all need to go and fight

00:31:44.340 --> 00:31:45.340
everyone

00:31:45.340 --> 00:31:46.340
bring your

00:31:46.340 --> 00:31:47.340
those who are fighters

00:31:47.340 --> 00:31:48.340
from amongst you

00:31:48.340 --> 00:31:49.340
we're going to

00:31:49.340 --> 00:31:50.340
Madina Munawwara

00:31:50.340 --> 00:31:51.340
so they had been joined

00:31:51.340 --> 00:31:52.340
by some of these tribes

00:31:52.340 --> 00:31:53.340
remember this name

00:31:53.340 --> 00:31:54.340
Banu al-Mustaliq

00:31:54.340 --> 00:31:55.340
the reason is later on

00:31:55.340 --> 00:31:57.340
the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:31:57.340 --> 00:31:58.340
went to attack them

00:31:58.340 --> 00:32:00.340
because they sided with Quraish

00:32:00.340 --> 00:32:02.340
and they came to attack the Muslims

00:32:02.340 --> 00:32:03.340
so when we had a chance

00:32:03.340 --> 00:32:04.340
we went back to tell them

00:32:04.340 --> 00:32:06.340
why did you take part

00:32:06.340 --> 00:32:07.340
on the wrong side

00:32:07.340 --> 00:32:09.340
the treaties always stated

00:32:09.340 --> 00:32:11.340
that those who sided with the enemy

00:32:11.340 --> 00:32:12.340
were considered enemy

00:32:12.340 --> 00:32:13.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:32:13.340 --> 00:32:15.340
protect us

00:32:16.340 --> 00:32:18.340
so as they marched

00:32:18.340 --> 00:32:19.340
they took together with them

00:32:19.340 --> 00:32:20.340
another man

00:32:20.340 --> 00:32:21.340
and his followers

00:32:21.340 --> 00:32:23.340
Abu Amir al-Rahim

00:32:23.340 --> 00:32:25.340
he was a man from Al-Aws

00:32:25.340 --> 00:32:26.340
and he was a person

00:32:26.340 --> 00:32:27.340
who was supposed to be

00:32:27.340 --> 00:32:28.340
one of the leaders

00:32:28.340 --> 00:32:29.340
in Madina Munawwara

00:32:29.340 --> 00:32:31.340
with Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:32:31.340 --> 00:32:32.340
and in fact

00:32:32.340 --> 00:32:33.340
when they were about to

00:32:33.340 --> 00:32:35.340
appoint Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:32:35.340 --> 00:32:37.340
then the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:32:37.340 --> 00:32:38.340
came to Madina Munawwara

00:32:38.340 --> 00:32:40.340
this Abu Amir ran away

00:32:40.340 --> 00:32:42.340
and as for Ubayy ibn Salul

00:32:42.340 --> 00:32:44.340
he decided to become

00:32:44.340 --> 00:32:45.340
a Muslim by name

00:32:45.340 --> 00:32:48.340
and yet he was not a Muslim

00:32:48.340 --> 00:32:50.340
so Abu Amir al-Rahim

00:32:50.340 --> 00:32:51.340
he joined the Quraish

00:32:51.340 --> 00:32:53.340
and he also proceeded

00:32:53.340 --> 00:32:55.340
to Madina Munawwara

00:32:55.340 --> 00:32:56.340
from amongst them

00:32:56.340 --> 00:32:58.340
was a man

00:32:58.340 --> 00:32:59.340
who was a slave of

00:32:59.340 --> 00:33:01.340
Jubayr ibn al-Mu'tain

00:33:01.340 --> 00:33:02.340
and his name was Wahshin

00:33:02.340 --> 00:33:04.340
this man was a slave

00:33:04.340 --> 00:33:06.340
from Abyssinia

00:33:06.340 --> 00:33:09.340
and his master told him

00:33:09.340 --> 00:33:10.340
that I will free you

00:33:10.340 --> 00:33:12.340
on condition that you

00:33:12.340 --> 00:33:16.340
execute Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib

00:33:16.340 --> 00:33:18.340
because he is the one

00:33:18.340 --> 00:33:20.340
who executed my uncle

00:33:20.340 --> 00:33:22.340
so Wahshi he was an innocent man

00:33:22.340 --> 00:33:23.340
he was a little slave

00:33:23.340 --> 00:33:24.340
but he decided

00:33:24.340 --> 00:33:25.340
look I need my freedom

00:33:25.340 --> 00:33:27.340
obviously I want to be a free man

00:33:27.340 --> 00:33:28.340
so let me go

00:33:28.340 --> 00:33:29.340
he also joined the ranks

00:33:29.340 --> 00:33:32.340
and then they arrived

00:33:32.340 --> 00:33:35.340
at a place close to Madina Munawwara

00:33:35.340 --> 00:33:36.340
just before Uhud

00:33:36.340 --> 00:33:38.340
and before they had arrived there

00:33:38.340 --> 00:33:40.340
the Messenger sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:33:40.340 --> 00:33:42.340
prepared his army

00:33:42.340 --> 00:33:43.340
and he had a system

00:33:43.340 --> 00:33:45.340
of preparing the army

00:33:45.340 --> 00:33:47.340
he got the people together

00:33:47.340 --> 00:33:48.340
he spoke to them

00:33:48.340 --> 00:33:49.340
he asked them

00:33:49.340 --> 00:33:50.340
look this is what it is

00:33:50.340 --> 00:33:51.340
we need to say

00:33:51.340 --> 00:33:53.340
hasbunallahu wa ni'mal wakil

00:33:53.340 --> 00:33:54.340
Allah is enough for us

00:33:54.340 --> 00:33:56.340
and definitely he is the best

00:33:56.340 --> 00:33:57.340
disposer of affairs

00:33:57.340 --> 00:33:58.340
this is a dua

00:33:58.340 --> 00:34:00.340
that Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:34:00.340 --> 00:34:02.340
had taught Muhammad sallallahu alayhi wa sallam

00:34:02.340 --> 00:34:04.340
who in turn taught the Muslims

00:34:04.340 --> 00:34:06.340
when something happens to you

00:34:06.340 --> 00:34:08.340
hasbunallahu wa ni'mal wakil

00:34:08.340 --> 00:34:09.340
Allah is enough for us

00:34:09.340 --> 00:34:11.340
and he is the best disposer of affairs

00:34:11.340 --> 00:34:13.340
so some of the people suggested

00:34:13.340 --> 00:34:15.340
let's stay in Madina

00:34:15.340 --> 00:34:17.340
we will fortify the place nicely

00:34:17.340 --> 00:34:18.340
and we will attack them

00:34:18.340 --> 00:34:20.340
from within Madina Munawwara

00:34:20.340 --> 00:34:22.340
who had this opinion?

00:34:22.340 --> 00:34:23.340
the older people

00:34:23.340 --> 00:34:25.340
some of the older people

00:34:25.340 --> 00:34:27.340
and Abdullah ibn Ubay ibn Salul

00:34:27.340 --> 00:34:28.340
that hypocrite

00:34:28.340 --> 00:34:30.340
he said no let's stay inside Madina

00:34:30.340 --> 00:34:31.340
and let the enemy come

00:34:31.340 --> 00:34:32.340
and we will attack them

00:34:32.340 --> 00:34:34.340
from within here

00:34:34.340 --> 00:34:35.340
and the youngsters

00:34:35.340 --> 00:34:36.340
a lot of the young people

00:34:36.340 --> 00:34:37.340
from amongst them was

00:34:37.340 --> 00:34:38.340
Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib as well

00:34:38.340 --> 00:34:39.340
who was a little bit older

00:34:39.340 --> 00:34:41.340
but he said let us go out

00:34:41.340 --> 00:34:42.340
and we face them outside

00:34:42.340 --> 00:34:43.340
because if we face them

00:34:43.340 --> 00:34:44.340
whilst we are inside

00:34:44.340 --> 00:34:45.340
if they win

00:34:45.340 --> 00:34:46.340
what will happen to our women

00:34:46.340 --> 00:34:47.340
and everyone else

00:34:47.340 --> 00:34:48.340
we'd rather go outside

00:34:48.340 --> 00:34:49.340
we face them there

00:34:49.340 --> 00:34:50.340
fight them there

00:34:50.340 --> 00:34:51.340
and sort the war out

00:34:51.340 --> 00:34:52.340
out there

00:34:52.340 --> 00:34:54.340
and thereafter it can be decided

00:34:54.340 --> 00:34:55.340
and we will not have

00:34:55.340 --> 00:34:56.340
to have them desecrate

00:34:56.340 --> 00:34:57.340
our homes here

00:34:57.340 --> 00:34:58.340
in Madina Munawwara

00:34:58.340 --> 00:34:59.340
and they kept on

00:34:59.340 --> 00:35:00.340
telling the messenger

00:35:00.340 --> 00:35:01.340
this is our opinion

00:35:01.340 --> 00:35:02.340
it's a more solid opinion

00:35:02.340 --> 00:35:03.340
we are the fighters

00:35:03.340 --> 00:35:04.340
we are going to be fighting

00:35:04.340 --> 00:35:05.340
we know

00:35:05.340 --> 00:35:06.340
we want to go out

00:35:06.340 --> 00:35:07.340
and so on

00:35:07.340 --> 00:35:08.340
until the Prophet

00:35:08.340 --> 00:35:09.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:35:09.340 --> 00:35:10.340
decided okay

00:35:10.340 --> 00:35:11.340
what will happen

00:35:11.340 --> 00:35:12.340
we will fight them outside

00:35:12.340 --> 00:35:13.340
let's all proceed

00:35:13.340 --> 00:35:14.340
and it is reported

00:35:14.340 --> 00:35:15.340
that on a Friday Jumu'ah

00:35:15.340 --> 00:35:16.340
the Prophet

00:35:16.340 --> 00:35:17.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:35:17.340 --> 00:35:18.340
took these men out

00:35:18.340 --> 00:35:19.340
and the Prophet

00:35:19.340 --> 00:35:20.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:35:20.340 --> 00:35:21.340
proceeded towards Badr

00:35:21.340 --> 00:35:22.340
sorry towards Uhud

00:35:22.340 --> 00:35:24.340
and Uhud is very very close

00:35:24.340 --> 00:35:25.340
now it is considered

00:35:25.340 --> 00:35:26.340
as inside Madina

00:35:26.340 --> 00:35:27.340
at that time

00:35:27.340 --> 00:35:28.340
it was outside

00:35:28.340 --> 00:35:29.340
Madina Munawwara

00:35:29.340 --> 00:35:31.340
and they took their time

00:35:31.340 --> 00:35:32.340
getting there

00:35:32.340 --> 00:35:34.340
so at Salat al-Jumu'ah

00:35:34.340 --> 00:35:35.340
the Prophet

00:35:35.340 --> 00:35:36.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:35:36.340 --> 00:35:37.340
led the Salat

00:35:37.340 --> 00:35:39.340
and he thereafter

00:35:39.340 --> 00:35:40.340
gave a Khutba to his people

00:35:40.340 --> 00:35:41.340
and he told them

00:35:41.340 --> 00:35:43.340
look we are going

00:35:43.340 --> 00:35:44.340
the idea here is

00:35:44.340 --> 00:35:45.340
to defend ourselves

00:35:45.340 --> 00:35:46.340
remember

00:35:46.340 --> 00:35:48.340
we did not initiate

00:35:48.340 --> 00:35:49.340
this battle

00:35:49.340 --> 00:35:50.340
it is them who are

00:35:50.340 --> 00:35:51.340
coming to us

00:35:51.340 --> 00:35:52.340
take a look

00:35:52.340 --> 00:35:53.340
Badr is closer to

00:35:53.340 --> 00:35:56.340
Madina than Mecca

00:35:56.340 --> 00:35:57.340
and Quraish wanted to fight

00:35:57.340 --> 00:35:58.340
although the Muslims

00:35:58.340 --> 00:35:59.340
went for the caravan

00:35:59.340 --> 00:36:00.340
but in this instance

00:36:00.340 --> 00:36:02.340
Quraish came all the way

00:36:02.340 --> 00:36:03.340
to fight the Muslims

00:36:03.340 --> 00:36:05.340
so who was the one

00:36:05.340 --> 00:36:06.340
who initiated it

00:36:06.340 --> 00:36:08.340
it was Quraish

00:36:08.340 --> 00:36:11.340
they came to Madina Munawwara

00:36:11.340 --> 00:36:12.340
and this is why the Prophet

00:36:12.340 --> 00:36:13.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:36:13.340 --> 00:36:14.340
all these people

00:36:14.340 --> 00:36:15.340
look we need to be disciplined

00:36:15.340 --> 00:36:16.340
we need to remember

00:36:16.340 --> 00:36:18.340
that Allah has granted us

00:36:18.340 --> 00:36:19.340
victory in the past

00:36:19.340 --> 00:36:20.340
through obedience

00:36:20.340 --> 00:36:21.340
so obey Allah

00:36:21.340 --> 00:36:22.340
and if you obey Allah

00:36:22.340 --> 00:36:23.340
Allah will help you

00:36:23.340 --> 00:36:25.340
and if you disobey Allah

00:36:25.340 --> 00:36:26.340
Shaytan will be with you

00:36:26.340 --> 00:36:27.340
so we ask Allah

00:36:27.340 --> 00:36:28.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:36:28.340 --> 00:36:30.340
to save us from Shaytan

00:36:30.340 --> 00:36:31.340
and the Prophet

00:36:31.340 --> 00:36:32.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:36:32.340 --> 00:36:34.340
thereafter

00:36:34.340 --> 00:36:38.340
he had taken 1,000 men with him

00:36:38.340 --> 00:36:39.340
1,000 men

00:36:39.340 --> 00:36:41.340
so the Mushriks

00:36:41.340 --> 00:36:43.340
were 3,000 heavily armed

00:36:43.340 --> 00:36:44.340
they came with everything

00:36:44.340 --> 00:36:45.340
they had had

00:36:45.340 --> 00:36:46.340
and they were on their way

00:36:46.340 --> 00:36:48.340
to Uhud almost there

00:36:48.340 --> 00:36:50.340
the Muslims 1,000 strong men

00:36:50.340 --> 00:36:52.340
and as they progressed

00:36:52.340 --> 00:36:53.340
the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:36:53.340 --> 00:36:55.340
thereafter

00:36:55.340 --> 00:36:58.340
had gone into one of the rooms

00:36:58.340 --> 00:37:00.340
and worn his armor

00:37:00.340 --> 00:37:01.340
he wore some of the armor

00:37:01.340 --> 00:37:03.340
that he used to wear

00:37:03.340 --> 00:37:04.340
and when he came out

00:37:04.340 --> 00:37:06.340
some of the older people

00:37:06.340 --> 00:37:07.340
told him

00:37:07.340 --> 00:37:08.340
you know

00:37:08.340 --> 00:37:09.340
we see that you are forced

00:37:09.340 --> 00:37:11.340
to leave Medina Munawwara

00:37:11.340 --> 00:37:12.340
by these young people

00:37:12.340 --> 00:37:13.340
it's okay

00:37:13.340 --> 00:37:14.340
let's go back in

00:37:14.340 --> 00:37:15.340
we won't fight

00:37:15.340 --> 00:37:16.340
we can perhaps

00:37:16.340 --> 00:37:17.340
look at a different way

00:37:17.340 --> 00:37:19.340
of dealing with these people

00:37:19.340 --> 00:37:20.340
he gave them a statement

00:37:20.340 --> 00:37:22.340
which was very powerful

00:37:22.340 --> 00:37:23.340
he says

00:37:23.340 --> 00:37:24.340
you should know

00:37:24.340 --> 00:37:26.340
that no messenger of Allah

00:37:26.340 --> 00:37:27.340
puts on an armor

00:37:27.340 --> 00:37:29.340
and then takes it off

00:37:29.340 --> 00:37:30.340
without facing that enemy

00:37:30.340 --> 00:37:31.340
may Allah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:37:31.340 --> 00:37:32.340
grant us

00:37:32.340 --> 00:37:33.340
an understanding

00:37:33.340 --> 00:37:35.340
no messenger of Allah

00:37:35.340 --> 00:37:37.340
has ever put on an armor

00:37:37.340 --> 00:37:38.340
and then removed it

00:37:38.340 --> 00:37:39.340
without Allah

00:37:39.340 --> 00:37:40.340
having decided between them

00:37:40.340 --> 00:37:41.340
and the enemy

00:37:41.340 --> 00:37:42.340
which means without them

00:37:42.340 --> 00:37:43.340
having fought

00:37:43.340 --> 00:37:44.340
may Allah sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:37:44.340 --> 00:37:45.340
protect us all

00:37:45.340 --> 00:37:47.340
so thereafter

00:37:47.340 --> 00:37:48.340
they proceeded

00:37:48.340 --> 00:37:50.340
and they got to a certain place

00:37:50.340 --> 00:37:52.340
where they camped

00:37:52.340 --> 00:37:53.340
for the evening

00:37:53.340 --> 00:37:54.340
in the meantime

00:37:54.340 --> 00:37:56.340
the Prophet sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:37:56.340 --> 00:37:58.340
had given the flags

00:37:58.340 --> 00:37:59.340
to three people

00:37:59.340 --> 00:38:00.340
the Muhajireen

00:38:00.340 --> 00:38:01.340
they had

00:38:01.340 --> 00:38:02.340
the biggest flag

00:38:02.340 --> 00:38:04.340
it was given to Mus'ab ibn Umayr

00:38:04.340 --> 00:38:05.340
it was considered

00:38:05.340 --> 00:38:06.340
the main flag

00:38:06.340 --> 00:38:07.340
which was the flag

00:38:07.340 --> 00:38:09.340
of the army of the Muslims

00:38:09.340 --> 00:38:11.340
and as for the Ansar

00:38:11.340 --> 00:38:12.340
they were divided into two

00:38:12.340 --> 00:38:14.340
the Khazraj

00:38:14.340 --> 00:38:15.340
the flag was given to

00:38:15.340 --> 00:38:17.340
Al-Hubab ibn Al-Munthir

00:38:17.340 --> 00:38:19.340
and Aws

00:38:19.340 --> 00:38:20.340
the flag was given to

00:38:20.340 --> 00:38:22.340
Usaid ibn Hudayr

00:38:22.340 --> 00:38:23.340
and these three

00:38:23.340 --> 00:38:24.340
had proceeded

00:38:24.340 --> 00:38:25.340
with the Muslim army

00:38:25.340 --> 00:38:26.340
for your information

00:38:26.340 --> 00:38:28.340
the flags were very important

00:38:28.340 --> 00:38:29.340
because

00:38:29.340 --> 00:38:31.340
when a flag was up

00:38:31.340 --> 00:38:32.340
it meant the army

00:38:32.340 --> 00:38:33.340
is still hot

00:38:33.340 --> 00:38:34.340
it's fighting

00:38:34.340 --> 00:38:35.340
and it has all its weaponry

00:38:35.340 --> 00:38:37.340
it has its strength

00:38:37.340 --> 00:38:39.340
once the flag drops

00:38:39.340 --> 00:38:41.340
the army is more or less confused

00:38:41.340 --> 00:38:42.340
because it's like

00:38:42.340 --> 00:38:43.340
the headquarters

00:38:43.340 --> 00:38:44.340
it's like we're looking

00:38:44.340 --> 00:38:45.340
for our leaders there

00:38:45.340 --> 00:38:46.340
so the flags were given

00:38:46.340 --> 00:38:47.340
to strategic people

00:38:47.340 --> 00:38:48.340
always

00:38:48.340 --> 00:38:49.340
even the Mushriks

00:38:49.340 --> 00:38:50.340
they had their flags

00:38:50.340 --> 00:38:51.340
which were given

00:38:51.340 --> 00:38:52.340
to strategic people

00:38:52.340 --> 00:38:53.340
from amongst them

00:38:53.340 --> 00:38:54.340
in this case

00:38:54.340 --> 00:38:55.340
I've given you the names

00:38:55.340 --> 00:38:56.340
the main flag

00:38:56.340 --> 00:38:57.340
was held by

00:38:57.340 --> 00:38:58.340
Mus'ad ibn Umayr

00:38:58.340 --> 00:38:59.340
r.a.

00:38:59.340 --> 00:39:01.340
when they got to Raqs al-Thaniyya

00:39:01.340 --> 00:39:03.340
that was a certain place

00:39:03.340 --> 00:39:04.340
Raqs al-Thaniyya

00:39:04.340 --> 00:39:05.340
is actually between

00:39:05.340 --> 00:39:06.340
Madinah and Uhud

00:39:06.340 --> 00:39:07.340
there is like a garden there

00:39:07.340 --> 00:39:09.340
as they got to the garden

00:39:09.340 --> 00:39:10.340
the Prophet s.a.w.

00:39:10.340 --> 00:39:11.340
saw a large

00:39:11.340 --> 00:39:12.340
battalion of people

00:39:12.340 --> 00:39:13.340
coming to join his army

00:39:13.340 --> 00:39:14.340
and he asked

00:39:14.340 --> 00:39:15.340
who are these?

00:39:15.340 --> 00:39:16.340
and he was told

00:39:16.340 --> 00:39:17.340
this is the group

00:39:17.340 --> 00:39:19.340
of Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:39:19.340 --> 00:39:20.340
from amongst them

00:39:20.340 --> 00:39:21.340
are the people of the book

00:39:21.340 --> 00:39:22.340
of the tribes

00:39:22.340 --> 00:39:23.340
the Jewish tribes

00:39:23.340 --> 00:39:24.340
who have settled here

00:39:24.340 --> 00:39:25.340
in Madinah

00:39:25.340 --> 00:39:26.340
the Prophet s.a.w.

00:39:26.340 --> 00:39:27.340
said

00:39:27.340 --> 00:39:28.340
tell them to go back

00:39:28.340 --> 00:39:29.340
we are not going

00:39:29.340 --> 00:39:30.340
to get their help

00:39:30.340 --> 00:39:31.340
to attack the Mushriks here

00:39:31.340 --> 00:39:32.340
Subhanallah

00:39:32.340 --> 00:39:33.340
we are not going

00:39:33.340 --> 00:39:34.340
to get their help

00:39:34.340 --> 00:39:35.340
to attack the Mushriks

00:39:35.340 --> 00:39:36.340
now

00:39:36.340 --> 00:39:37.340
there was some reasoning

00:39:37.340 --> 00:39:38.340
behind it

00:39:38.340 --> 00:39:39.340
because as it is

00:39:39.340 --> 00:39:40.340
there was disturbance

00:39:40.340 --> 00:39:41.340
these people

00:39:41.340 --> 00:39:42.340
could have been

00:39:42.340 --> 00:39:43.340
part of the enemy

00:39:43.340 --> 00:39:44.340
without us knowing

00:39:44.340 --> 00:39:45.340
and they could have

00:39:45.340 --> 00:39:46.340
come in the ranks

00:39:46.340 --> 00:39:47.340
and then caused

00:39:47.340 --> 00:39:48.340
a lot of destruction

00:39:48.340 --> 00:39:49.340
so the Prophet s.a.w.

00:39:49.340 --> 00:39:50.340
sent them all back

00:39:50.340 --> 00:39:52.340
and they had gone back

00:39:52.340 --> 00:39:53.340
the group of people

00:39:53.340 --> 00:39:54.340
who were allied

00:39:54.340 --> 00:39:55.340
to

00:39:55.340 --> 00:39:57.340
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:39:57.340 --> 00:39:59.340
and as for Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:39:59.340 --> 00:40:02.340
after they had spent that night

00:40:02.340 --> 00:40:04.340
after they had spent the night

00:40:04.340 --> 00:40:06.340
the Prophet s.a.w.

00:40:06.340 --> 00:40:08.340
in early morning decided

00:40:08.340 --> 00:40:09.340
let us now go

00:40:09.340 --> 00:40:10.340
towards Uhud

00:40:10.340 --> 00:40:12.340
and as he was going

00:40:12.340 --> 00:40:14.340
the last leg of the journey

00:40:14.340 --> 00:40:16.340
it's not a very long journey

00:40:16.340 --> 00:40:18.340
Abdullah ibn Ubayy decides

00:40:18.340 --> 00:40:20.340
with 300 men

00:40:20.340 --> 00:40:21.340
we are going back to Madinah

00:40:21.340 --> 00:40:22.340
we are not fighting

00:40:22.340 --> 00:40:23.340
why?

00:40:23.340 --> 00:40:24.340
we are not fighting

00:40:24.340 --> 00:40:25.340
we are not fighting

00:40:25.340 --> 00:40:26.340
because we told you

00:40:26.340 --> 00:40:27.340
we don't want to fight

00:40:27.340 --> 00:40:28.340
we told you

00:40:28.340 --> 00:40:29.340
that we would like

00:40:29.340 --> 00:40:30.340
to stay in Madinah

00:40:30.340 --> 00:40:32.340
we are older people

00:40:32.340 --> 00:40:33.340
and you listened

00:40:33.340 --> 00:40:34.340
to the youngsters

00:40:34.340 --> 00:40:35.340
you listened to those

00:40:35.340 --> 00:40:36.340
who don't really

00:40:36.340 --> 00:40:37.340
have much experience

00:40:37.340 --> 00:40:38.340
and you came out

00:40:38.340 --> 00:40:39.340
why should we come out?

00:40:39.340 --> 00:40:41.340
so we are going back

00:40:41.340 --> 00:40:43.340
now this was a big problem

00:40:43.340 --> 00:40:44.340
very big problem

00:40:44.340 --> 00:40:47.340
because one third of the army

00:40:47.340 --> 00:40:48.340
of the Muslims

00:40:48.340 --> 00:40:49.340
is going back

00:40:49.340 --> 00:40:50.340
and with them is

00:40:50.340 --> 00:40:52.340
Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:40:52.340 --> 00:40:53.340
so he was indeed

00:40:53.340 --> 00:40:54.340
part of the enemy

00:40:54.340 --> 00:40:56.340
and he was part of the problem

00:40:56.340 --> 00:40:57.340
so now what happened?

00:40:57.340 --> 00:40:59.340
some of the tribes

00:40:59.340 --> 00:41:01.340
almost joined him

00:41:01.340 --> 00:41:03.340
some of the tribes of the Ansar

00:41:03.340 --> 00:41:04.340
almost joined him

00:41:04.340 --> 00:41:06.340
but Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:41:06.340 --> 00:41:07.340
granted them strength

00:41:07.340 --> 00:41:08.340
so with him were

00:41:08.340 --> 00:41:10.340
300 people who were all

00:41:10.340 --> 00:41:11.340
close to him

00:41:11.340 --> 00:41:12.340
and connected to him

00:41:12.340 --> 00:41:13.340
in one way or the other

00:41:13.340 --> 00:41:14.340
and they had gone back

00:41:14.340 --> 00:41:15.340
to Madinah and Munawwar

00:41:15.340 --> 00:41:16.340
or they decided to go back

00:41:16.340 --> 00:41:18.340
and Allah protected the rest

00:41:18.340 --> 00:41:20.340
however

00:41:20.340 --> 00:41:22.340
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:41:22.340 --> 00:41:25.340
had revealed verses later on

00:41:25.340 --> 00:41:26.340
to tell us

00:41:26.340 --> 00:41:27.340
and to instruct us

00:41:27.340 --> 00:41:28.340
what had happened

00:41:28.340 --> 00:41:29.340
to tell us what has happened

00:41:29.340 --> 00:41:31.340
there one of the sahabah

00:41:31.340 --> 00:41:33.340
radiallahu anhum

00:41:33.340 --> 00:41:35.340
the father of Jabir ibn Abdullah

00:41:35.340 --> 00:41:37.340
radiallahu anhum

00:41:37.340 --> 00:41:39.340
he went to Abdullah ibn Ubayy

00:41:39.340 --> 00:41:40.340
and he tried to tell him

00:41:40.340 --> 00:41:41.340
look come back

00:41:41.340 --> 00:41:43.340
how can you decide to do this?

00:41:43.340 --> 00:41:44.340
we are all out here

00:41:44.340 --> 00:41:45.340
we accepted the messenger

00:41:45.340 --> 00:41:47.340
we told him we would

00:41:47.340 --> 00:41:48.340
protect him

00:41:48.340 --> 00:41:49.340
we said that we would

00:41:49.340 --> 00:41:50.340
protect Madinah

00:41:50.340 --> 00:41:51.340
and so on

00:41:51.340 --> 00:41:52.340
and now you want to

00:41:52.340 --> 00:41:55.340
go away

00:41:55.340 --> 00:41:56.340
and the Muslims were

00:41:56.340 --> 00:41:57.340
divided into two groups

00:41:57.340 --> 00:41:59.340
some of them said no

00:41:59.340 --> 00:42:01.340
let us stop everything

00:42:01.340 --> 00:42:03.340
and fight Abdullah ibn Ubayy

00:42:03.340 --> 00:42:04.340
we are 700 odd

00:42:04.340 --> 00:42:06.340
they are 300 odd

00:42:06.340 --> 00:42:08.340
we fight them here and now

00:42:08.340 --> 00:42:10.340
and the other group said no

00:42:10.340 --> 00:42:11.340
leave them for now

00:42:11.340 --> 00:42:12.340
we have a bigger enemy

00:42:12.340 --> 00:42:13.340
to go and to deal with

00:42:13.340 --> 00:42:14.340
so you see there is

00:42:14.340 --> 00:42:15.340
already a crack

00:42:15.340 --> 00:42:17.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:42:17.340 --> 00:42:18.340
protect us

00:42:18.340 --> 00:42:19.340
and at this point

00:42:19.340 --> 00:42:21.340
Allah reveals verses

00:42:42.340 --> 00:42:43.340
what is it with you?

00:42:43.340 --> 00:42:44.340
how can you dispute

00:42:44.340 --> 00:42:45.340
about the hypocrites?

00:42:45.340 --> 00:42:47.340
when Allah sent them back

00:42:47.340 --> 00:42:48.340
because of their deeds

00:42:48.340 --> 00:42:50.340
they had evil deeds

00:42:50.340 --> 00:42:51.340
Allah did not want them

00:42:51.340 --> 00:42:52.340
to take part in the battle

00:42:52.340 --> 00:42:53.340
so Allah is the one

00:42:53.340 --> 00:42:55.340
who sent them back

00:42:55.340 --> 00:42:56.340
Allahu Akbar

00:42:56.340 --> 00:42:57.340
and Allah says

00:42:57.340 --> 00:42:59.340
when Allah misguides someone

00:42:59.340 --> 00:43:00.340
nobody can guide him

00:43:00.340 --> 00:43:02.340
they want you to disbelieve

00:43:02.340 --> 00:43:03.340
just like they disbelieve

00:43:03.340 --> 00:43:04.340
so don't even turn

00:43:04.340 --> 00:43:05.340
towards them

00:43:05.340 --> 00:43:06.340
and at that stage

00:43:06.340 --> 00:43:07.340
they were left

00:43:07.340 --> 00:43:08.340
they were told to go back

00:43:08.340 --> 00:43:10.340
that saved a huge difficulty

00:43:10.340 --> 00:43:11.340
because the Muslims

00:43:11.340 --> 00:43:12.340
were deciding to fight them

00:43:12.340 --> 00:43:13.340
and Allah said

00:43:13.340 --> 00:43:14.340
leave them alone

00:43:14.340 --> 00:43:15.340
let them go back

00:43:15.340 --> 00:43:16.340
they are the hypocrites

00:43:16.340 --> 00:43:17.340
and so on

00:43:17.340 --> 00:43:18.340
and these verses

00:43:18.340 --> 00:43:19.340
were extremely powerful

00:43:19.340 --> 00:43:21.340
and decisive at the same time

00:43:21.340 --> 00:43:24.340
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:43:24.340 --> 00:43:25.340
as he had come out

00:43:25.340 --> 00:43:26.340
and we made mention

00:43:26.340 --> 00:43:27.340
of 300 people going back

00:43:27.340 --> 00:43:29.340
with Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salul

00:43:29.340 --> 00:43:32.340
it was Abdullah ibn Amr ibn Haram

00:43:32.340 --> 00:43:33.340
who had spoken to him

00:43:33.340 --> 00:43:34.340
and thereafter

00:43:34.340 --> 00:43:35.340
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:43:35.340 --> 00:43:36.340
revealed the verses

00:43:36.340 --> 00:43:38.340
that I had just read out to you

00:43:38.340 --> 00:43:39.340
and after that

00:43:39.340 --> 00:43:41.340
the army proceeded to Uhud

00:43:41.340 --> 00:43:43.340
when they arrived in Uhud

00:43:43.340 --> 00:43:44.340
they scouted the place

00:43:44.340 --> 00:43:45.340
and they saw it

00:43:45.340 --> 00:43:46.340
and they decided

00:43:46.340 --> 00:43:49.340
we are going to stand in a way

00:43:49.340 --> 00:43:51.340
that we will be facing Medina

00:43:51.340 --> 00:43:53.340
and the mountain will be behind us

00:43:53.340 --> 00:43:56.340
so they were facing Medina Munawwara

00:43:56.340 --> 00:43:57.340
and they stood in a way

00:43:57.340 --> 00:43:59.340
that the mountain was behind them

00:43:59.340 --> 00:44:01.340
when the Kuffar had come around

00:44:01.340 --> 00:44:03.340
they were on the other side of the valley

00:44:03.340 --> 00:44:04.340
they came and they stood

00:44:04.340 --> 00:44:05.340
on the other side

00:44:05.340 --> 00:44:07.340
so their backs

00:44:07.340 --> 00:44:09.340
were facing Medina Munawwara

00:44:09.340 --> 00:44:12.340
and the front was facing the mountain

00:44:12.340 --> 00:44:14.340
and the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:44:14.340 --> 00:44:15.340
as always

00:44:15.340 --> 00:44:17.340
he gave a lecture

00:44:17.340 --> 00:44:18.340
powerful lecture to his people

00:44:18.340 --> 00:44:20.340
short but to the point

00:44:20.340 --> 00:44:21.340
he says look

00:44:21.340 --> 00:44:22.340
your sustenance is written

00:44:22.340 --> 00:44:24.340
by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:44:24.340 --> 00:44:25.340
you will not die

00:44:25.340 --> 00:44:27.340
until everything written

00:44:27.340 --> 00:44:29.340
next to your name gets to you

00:44:29.340 --> 00:44:30.340
so don't think that

00:44:30.340 --> 00:44:32.340
by making haste to get something

00:44:32.340 --> 00:44:33.340
you are actually going to increase

00:44:33.340 --> 00:44:34.340
your sustenance

00:44:34.340 --> 00:44:35.340
no

00:44:35.340 --> 00:44:36.340
what Allah has written for you

00:44:36.340 --> 00:44:37.340
will come to you

00:44:37.340 --> 00:44:39.340
so be careful

00:44:39.340 --> 00:44:42.340
and fear Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:44:42.340 --> 00:44:43.340
and at the same time

00:44:43.340 --> 00:44:45.340
obey instructions

00:44:45.340 --> 00:44:46.340
for it is the obedience

00:44:46.340 --> 00:44:49.340
that granted us victory in Badr

00:44:49.340 --> 00:44:51.340
how did we get victory in Badr

00:44:51.340 --> 00:44:52.340
obedience

00:44:52.340 --> 00:44:54.340
they obeyed Allah in His instruction

00:44:54.340 --> 00:44:55.340
when Allah told them go to Badr

00:44:55.340 --> 00:44:56.340
they all went

00:44:56.340 --> 00:44:57.340
when Allah said

00:44:57.340 --> 00:44:58.340
you will now fight these people

00:44:58.340 --> 00:44:59.340
they all fought

00:44:59.340 --> 00:45:00.340
so now

00:45:00.340 --> 00:45:01.340
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:45:01.340 --> 00:45:02.340
warned them

00:45:02.340 --> 00:45:04.340
he gave them a powerful lecture

00:45:04.340 --> 00:45:06.340
and thereafter

00:45:06.340 --> 00:45:08.340
he had placed the rose

00:45:08.340 --> 00:45:09.340
as he always places

00:45:09.340 --> 00:45:11.340
with those who were

00:45:12.340 --> 00:45:13.340
who had the arrows

00:45:13.340 --> 00:45:14.340
and bows in the front

00:45:14.340 --> 00:45:16.340
and the horse men behind

00:45:16.340 --> 00:45:17.340
and thereafter

00:45:17.340 --> 00:45:20.340
you have a new group of people

00:45:20.340 --> 00:45:23.340
because there was a mountain

00:45:23.340 --> 00:45:25.340
behind them

00:45:25.340 --> 00:45:26.340
there was a mountain

00:45:26.340 --> 00:45:27.340
behind them

00:45:27.340 --> 00:45:28.340
the Mount Uhud

00:45:28.340 --> 00:45:30.340
Mount Uhud is a huge mountain

00:45:30.340 --> 00:45:31.340
and it has a few hillocks

00:45:31.340 --> 00:45:32.340
around it

00:45:32.340 --> 00:45:34.340
so the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:45:34.340 --> 00:45:36.340
when he studied Uhud

00:45:36.340 --> 00:45:39.340
he placed between 40 and 50 archers

00:45:39.340 --> 00:45:41.340
some most of the narration say 50

00:45:41.340 --> 00:45:44.340
some of them say between 40 and 50

00:45:44.340 --> 00:45:47.340
he placed these archers on the hillock

00:45:47.340 --> 00:45:50.340
and the head of these archers

00:45:50.340 --> 00:45:51.340
was a man known as

00:45:51.340 --> 00:45:53.340
Abdullah ibn Jubayr al-Ansari

00:45:53.340 --> 00:45:54.340
powerful man

00:45:54.340 --> 00:45:55.340
the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:45:55.340 --> 00:45:57.340
told him in front of all the archers

00:45:57.340 --> 00:46:00.340
look we are placing you on this hillock

00:46:00.340 --> 00:46:03.340
you are here to protect our backs

00:46:03.340 --> 00:46:05.340
if you see we are winning

00:46:05.340 --> 00:46:06.340
don't leave this mount

00:46:06.340 --> 00:46:08.340
if you see we are losing

00:46:08.340 --> 00:46:09.340
don't leave this mount

00:46:09.340 --> 00:46:11.340
no matter what happens

00:46:11.340 --> 00:46:12.340
do not leave this mount

00:46:12.340 --> 00:46:13.340
that's the instruction

00:46:13.340 --> 00:46:16.340
because this is a strategic place

00:46:16.340 --> 00:46:19.340
from which the enemy can attack

00:46:19.340 --> 00:46:21.340
they understood it very carefully mashaAllah

00:46:21.340 --> 00:46:23.340
and they were also very active

00:46:23.340 --> 00:46:24.340
with their spears and arrows

00:46:24.340 --> 00:46:25.340
from the top there

00:46:25.340 --> 00:46:26.340
Alhamdulillah

00:46:26.340 --> 00:46:29.340
and as we mentioned yesterday

00:46:29.340 --> 00:46:30.340
or previously when we spoke

00:46:30.340 --> 00:46:32.340
of the battle of Badr

00:46:32.340 --> 00:46:34.340
they started with the duels

00:46:34.340 --> 00:46:36.340
this time it was slightly different

00:46:36.340 --> 00:46:37.340
in the sense that

00:46:37.340 --> 00:46:39.340
previously three came out from the Mushriks

00:46:39.340 --> 00:46:42.340
three came out from the Muslims

00:46:42.340 --> 00:46:44.340
this time one of the men

00:46:44.340 --> 00:46:45.340
came out from the Mushriks

00:46:45.340 --> 00:46:48.340
and immediately as he came out

00:46:48.340 --> 00:46:50.340
Az-Zubayr ibn al-Awwam

00:46:50.340 --> 00:46:51.340
came out to him

00:46:51.340 --> 00:46:52.340
executed him

00:46:52.340 --> 00:46:53.340
they were shocked

00:46:53.340 --> 00:46:55.340
within a minute the war had started

00:46:55.340 --> 00:46:57.340
but the two armies

00:46:57.340 --> 00:46:59.340
one was on the side

00:46:59.340 --> 00:47:00.340
closer to Madina

00:47:00.340 --> 00:47:01.340
and the other one was on the side

00:47:01.340 --> 00:47:03.340
closer to Mecca

00:47:03.340 --> 00:47:05.340
and one man is already gone

00:47:05.340 --> 00:47:07.340
this is the duel that they had had

00:47:07.340 --> 00:47:09.340
so immediately after that

00:47:09.340 --> 00:47:12.340
Talha ibn Abi Talha came out

00:47:12.340 --> 00:47:13.340
and as he came out

00:47:13.340 --> 00:47:16.340
he was a Mushrik from the Meccan army

00:47:16.340 --> 00:47:18.340
Ali ibn Abi Talib radiallahu anhu

00:47:18.340 --> 00:47:19.340
came out and executed him

00:47:19.340 --> 00:47:22.340
within a minute he was also gone

00:47:22.340 --> 00:47:23.340
now his son decides

00:47:23.340 --> 00:47:24.340
let me come out

00:47:24.340 --> 00:47:25.340
in fact his brother

00:47:25.340 --> 00:47:27.340
Uthman ibn Abi Talha

00:47:27.340 --> 00:47:28.340
he was also a Mushrik

00:47:28.340 --> 00:47:29.340
as he came out

00:47:29.340 --> 00:47:30.340
Hamza radiallahu anhu

00:47:30.340 --> 00:47:32.340
came out and executed him

00:47:32.340 --> 00:47:33.340
and the Mushriks are watching

00:47:33.340 --> 00:47:34.340
and they are shocked

00:47:34.340 --> 00:47:35.340
because one after the other

00:47:35.340 --> 00:47:36.340
they started losing

00:47:36.340 --> 00:47:37.340
losing their men

00:47:37.340 --> 00:47:39.340
and thereafter

00:47:39.340 --> 00:47:41.340
Abu Sa'ad ibn Abi Talha

00:47:41.340 --> 00:47:43.340
another brother came out

00:47:43.340 --> 00:47:45.340
so Sa'ad ibn Abi Waqas

00:47:45.340 --> 00:47:46.340
hit him with an arrow

00:47:46.340 --> 00:47:48.340
or with a spear

00:47:48.340 --> 00:47:49.340
and he also dropped

00:47:49.340 --> 00:47:51.340
executed, gone

00:47:51.340 --> 00:47:52.340
thereafter

00:47:52.340 --> 00:47:54.340
four of the members

00:47:54.340 --> 00:47:55.340
of the same family

00:47:55.340 --> 00:47:56.340
one after the other

00:47:56.340 --> 00:47:57.340
came out

00:47:57.340 --> 00:47:58.340
each one of them was wiped

00:47:58.340 --> 00:48:00.340
as they came

00:48:00.340 --> 00:48:01.340
and then the Mushriks

00:48:01.340 --> 00:48:03.340
became so upset

00:48:03.340 --> 00:48:05.340
and it resulted in them

00:48:05.340 --> 00:48:06.340
becoming so angry

00:48:06.340 --> 00:48:08.340
they started charging forward

00:48:08.340 --> 00:48:09.340
with their horses

00:48:09.340 --> 00:48:10.340
and as they charged forward

00:48:10.340 --> 00:48:12.340
they got to a place

00:48:12.340 --> 00:48:13.340
where the arrows were released

00:48:13.340 --> 00:48:14.340
by the Muslims

00:48:14.340 --> 00:48:15.340
as they were released

00:48:15.340 --> 00:48:16.340
in Badr

00:48:16.340 --> 00:48:17.340
and the horses were struck

00:48:17.340 --> 00:48:19.340
and that caused great chaos

00:48:19.340 --> 00:48:21.340
and the horses began to go back

00:48:21.340 --> 00:48:22.340
some of them had dropped

00:48:22.340 --> 00:48:23.340
people started losing their lives

00:48:23.340 --> 00:48:24.340
and it was only

00:48:24.340 --> 00:48:26.340
the beginning of this battle

00:48:26.340 --> 00:48:27.340
so quick

00:48:27.340 --> 00:48:28.340
everything started happening

00:48:28.340 --> 00:48:29.340
very very quickly

00:48:29.340 --> 00:48:30.340
and thereafter

00:48:30.340 --> 00:48:32.340
there was a hot struggle

00:48:32.340 --> 00:48:33.340
when I say hot

00:48:33.340 --> 00:48:34.340
I mean the heat of the moment

00:48:34.340 --> 00:48:35.340
what had happened is

00:48:35.340 --> 00:48:36.340
Wahshi says

00:48:36.340 --> 00:48:37.340
later on

00:48:37.340 --> 00:48:38.340
he became a Muslim

00:48:38.340 --> 00:48:39.340
some time later

00:48:39.340 --> 00:48:40.340
he was the slave

00:48:40.340 --> 00:48:41.340
of Jubayr ibn al-Mutaim

00:48:41.340 --> 00:48:42.340
he says

00:48:42.340 --> 00:48:43.340
I was watching Hamza

00:48:43.340 --> 00:48:44.340
because I had seen him

00:48:44.340 --> 00:48:45.340
from the duel

00:48:45.340 --> 00:48:47.340
and I knew who he was

00:48:47.340 --> 00:48:48.340
and as I'm watching him

00:48:48.340 --> 00:48:49.340
I moved to the side

00:48:49.340 --> 00:48:50.340
I moved to this side

00:48:50.340 --> 00:48:51.340
I had no other job

00:48:51.340 --> 00:48:52.340
I did not harm anyone

00:48:52.340 --> 00:48:53.340
no one

00:48:53.340 --> 00:48:54.340
nothing else did I do

00:48:54.340 --> 00:48:56.340
besides holding one spear

00:48:56.340 --> 00:48:57.340
and waiting for one man

00:48:57.340 --> 00:48:58.340
and he says

00:48:58.340 --> 00:48:59.340
when I found him alone

00:48:59.340 --> 00:49:00.340
at a certain place

00:49:00.340 --> 00:49:01.340
I hit him

00:49:01.340 --> 00:49:02.340
and it hit his belly

00:49:02.340 --> 00:49:03.340
according to one narration

00:49:03.340 --> 00:49:04.340
just below his navel

00:49:04.340 --> 00:49:05.340
and he says

00:49:05.340 --> 00:49:06.340
I dropped him

00:49:06.340 --> 00:49:07.340
he was down cold

00:49:07.340 --> 00:49:08.340
and I was done

00:49:08.340 --> 00:49:09.340
Allahu Akbar

00:49:09.340 --> 00:49:10.340
Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib

00:49:10.340 --> 00:49:11.340
who was known as Asadullah

00:49:11.340 --> 00:49:12.340
the lion of Allah

00:49:12.340 --> 00:49:13.340
subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:49:13.340 --> 00:49:14.340
he was also known as

00:49:14.340 --> 00:49:15.340
Sayyid al-Shuhada

00:49:15.340 --> 00:49:16.340
he was also known as

00:49:16.340 --> 00:49:17.340
the leader of the martyrs

00:49:17.340 --> 00:49:18.340
subhanallah

00:49:18.340 --> 00:49:19.340
he was also known as

00:49:19.340 --> 00:49:20.340
Sayyid al-Shuhada

00:49:20.340 --> 00:49:21.340
he was also known as

00:49:21.340 --> 00:49:22.340
the leader of the martyrs

00:49:22.340 --> 00:49:23.340
subhanallah

00:49:23.340 --> 00:49:24.340
he was also known as

00:49:24.340 --> 00:49:25.340
the leader of the martyrs

00:49:25.340 --> 00:49:26.340
subhanallah

00:49:26.340 --> 00:49:27.340
subhanallah

00:49:27.340 --> 00:49:28.340
he was martyred

00:49:28.340 --> 00:49:29.340
in the battle of Uhud

00:49:29.340 --> 00:49:31.340
and the one who killed him

00:49:31.340 --> 00:49:32.340
his name was Wahshi

00:49:32.340 --> 00:49:33.340
he did it

00:49:33.340 --> 00:49:34.340
because he wanted to

00:49:34.340 --> 00:49:35.340
earn his freedom

00:49:35.340 --> 00:49:37.340
and Hamza ibn Abdul Muttalib

00:49:37.340 --> 00:49:38.340
radiallahu anhu

00:49:38.340 --> 00:49:39.340
was martyred

00:49:39.340 --> 00:49:44.340
and the war became such

00:49:44.340 --> 00:49:45.340
that the mushrik

00:49:45.340 --> 00:49:48.340
started losing one after the other

00:49:48.340 --> 00:49:50.340
they were losing a lot

00:49:50.340 --> 00:49:52.340
and as they were losing

00:49:52.340 --> 00:49:55.340
they decided to turn back

00:49:55.340 --> 00:49:57.340
and to flee

00:49:57.340 --> 00:49:59.340
and so they started running away

00:49:59.340 --> 00:50:00.340
the people of Makkah

00:50:00.340 --> 00:50:02.340
as many as they were

00:50:02.340 --> 00:50:03.340
they started running away

00:50:03.340 --> 00:50:06.340
leaving behind a lot of their belongings

00:50:06.340 --> 00:50:08.340
when they started running away

00:50:08.340 --> 00:50:09.340
some of the Muslims

00:50:09.340 --> 00:50:10.340
began to gather

00:50:10.340 --> 00:50:12.340
some of the belongings

00:50:12.340 --> 00:50:13.340
of the mushrik

00:50:13.340 --> 00:50:14.340
thinking that let's get it

00:50:14.340 --> 00:50:15.340
and put it on one side

00:50:15.340 --> 00:50:17.340
so that we know where it is

00:50:17.340 --> 00:50:18.340
and so on

00:50:18.340 --> 00:50:21.340
and thereafter

00:50:21.340 --> 00:50:22.340
Allahu Akbar

00:50:22.340 --> 00:50:24.340
something very dangerous happened

00:50:24.340 --> 00:50:27.340
which changed the course of the whole war

00:50:27.340 --> 00:50:30.340
Abdullah ibn Jubayr al-Ansari

00:50:30.340 --> 00:50:31.340
who was the head of the archers

00:50:31.340 --> 00:50:32.340
on that mount

00:50:32.340 --> 00:50:35.340
found that some of his men insisted

00:50:35.340 --> 00:50:37.340
now the war is over

00:50:37.340 --> 00:50:38.340
let's go down

00:50:38.340 --> 00:50:39.340
and start collecting and gathering

00:50:39.340 --> 00:50:40.340
he said no

00:50:40.340 --> 00:50:42.340
the instruction of the messenger was this

00:50:42.340 --> 00:50:43.340
remain here

00:50:43.340 --> 00:50:44.340
they said no no no

00:50:44.340 --> 00:50:45.340
the war is over

00:50:45.340 --> 00:50:46.340
let's go

00:50:46.340 --> 00:50:47.340
so what had happened

00:50:47.340 --> 00:50:49.340
a lot of them went

00:50:49.340 --> 00:50:51.340
and they left the hillock

00:50:51.340 --> 00:50:52.340
when they left the hillock

00:50:52.340 --> 00:50:54.340
Abdullah

00:50:54.340 --> 00:50:55.340
Allahu Akbar

00:50:55.340 --> 00:50:58.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant them goodness

00:50:58.340 --> 00:51:00.340
these people who had remained behind

00:51:00.340 --> 00:51:02.340
Abdullah ibn Jubayr al-Ansari

00:51:02.340 --> 00:51:03.340
and a few of the people

00:51:03.340 --> 00:51:06.340
they found Khalid ibn Walid

00:51:06.340 --> 00:51:08.340
who was from amongst the mushrik at the time

00:51:08.340 --> 00:51:10.340
he had a little battalion with him

00:51:10.340 --> 00:51:13.340
when he saw that these people are no longer on the hillock

00:51:13.340 --> 00:51:15.340
he decided to come around

00:51:15.340 --> 00:51:18.340
and he came onto that mount

00:51:18.340 --> 00:51:21.340
and they executed all of the remainder of the archers

00:51:21.340 --> 00:51:22.340
who were very few

00:51:22.340 --> 00:51:25.340
including Abdullah ibn Jubayr al-Ansari

00:51:25.340 --> 00:51:27.340
and what had happened is

00:51:27.340 --> 00:51:30.340
he came and sandwiched the Muslims

00:51:30.340 --> 00:51:33.340
between the enemy who now turned around

00:51:33.340 --> 00:51:35.340
when they had heard a new noise

00:51:35.340 --> 00:51:39.340
and they then came and they began to attack the Muslims

00:51:39.340 --> 00:51:43.340
and this is when the Muslims suffered great losses on that day

00:51:43.340 --> 00:51:46.340
although there was no decisive victor

00:51:46.340 --> 00:51:49.340
because the Muslims continued fighting

00:51:49.340 --> 00:51:51.340
people began to lose their lives

00:51:51.340 --> 00:51:54.340
and from amongst them Mus'ab ibn Umayr radiallahu anhu

00:51:54.340 --> 00:51:57.340
who was holding the flag

00:51:57.340 --> 00:51:59.340
they chopped off one of his hands

00:51:59.340 --> 00:52:00.340
so he held it with the other hand

00:52:00.340 --> 00:52:01.340
they sliced his other hand

00:52:01.340 --> 00:52:05.340
so he put it close to his chest until they executed him

00:52:05.340 --> 00:52:06.340
and the flag dropped

00:52:06.340 --> 00:52:09.340
and news spread that Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:52:09.340 --> 00:52:10.340
has been killed

00:52:10.340 --> 00:52:12.340
and when that happened

00:52:12.340 --> 00:52:14.340
there was a lot of chaos in the Muslim army

00:52:14.340 --> 00:52:18.340
and thereafter the kuffar began to kill a lot of people

00:52:18.340 --> 00:52:20.340
and the sahabah radiallahu anhu

00:52:20.340 --> 00:52:22.340
was surrounding Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:52:22.340 --> 00:52:25.340
taking the arrows and spears for him

00:52:25.340 --> 00:52:27.340
and a lot of them lost their lives in that way

00:52:27.340 --> 00:52:29.340
and thereafter you find

00:52:29.340 --> 00:52:32.340
the arrows hit Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:52:32.340 --> 00:52:33.340
on his face

00:52:33.340 --> 00:52:36.340
and he had marks on his cheeks

00:52:36.340 --> 00:52:38.340
and he had a gash on his head

00:52:38.340 --> 00:52:41.340
and at the same time a rock was thrown on him

00:52:41.340 --> 00:52:43.340
and what happened is

00:52:43.340 --> 00:52:45.340
the name of the man who threw the rock

00:52:46.340 --> 00:52:50.340
he threw this rock on Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:52:50.340 --> 00:52:52.340
which broke his tooth

00:52:52.340 --> 00:52:55.340
and Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam was bleeding

00:52:55.340 --> 00:52:58.340
and thereafter you find a man known as

00:52:58.340 --> 00:52:59.340
Ubayy ibn Khalaf

00:52:59.340 --> 00:53:01.340
he was an enemy of Islam

00:53:01.340 --> 00:53:04.340
from the beginning the days of Makkah

00:53:04.340 --> 00:53:05.340
he told the messenger

00:53:05.340 --> 00:53:06.340
I will kill you

00:53:06.340 --> 00:53:08.340
and Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam says

00:53:08.340 --> 00:53:10.340
Inshallah it will be the other way round

00:53:10.340 --> 00:53:13.340
so he was now coming for Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:53:14.340 --> 00:53:18.340
and the Sahaba are protecting Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:53:18.340 --> 00:53:20.340
and Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam said

00:53:20.340 --> 00:53:22.340
leave him, let him come

00:53:22.340 --> 00:53:25.340
and the prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam took a spear

00:53:25.340 --> 00:53:27.340
and threw it which hit him

00:53:27.340 --> 00:53:30.340
to the degree that later on when he was running away

00:53:30.340 --> 00:53:31.340
he died

00:53:31.340 --> 00:53:34.340
it is reported that this was the only person ever

00:53:34.340 --> 00:53:37.340
who died as a result of being struck

00:53:37.340 --> 00:53:39.340
by Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:53:39.340 --> 00:53:42.340
no one else in the life of Muhammad sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:53:42.340 --> 00:53:43.340
was ever struck

00:53:43.340 --> 00:53:45.340
which resulted in their death

00:53:45.340 --> 00:53:47.340
by Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:53:47.340 --> 00:53:49.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us an understanding

00:53:49.340 --> 00:53:51.340
and may he grant us goodness

00:53:51.340 --> 00:53:53.340
it is important for me to make mention

00:53:53.340 --> 00:53:55.340
that the Muslims retreated

00:53:55.340 --> 00:53:56.340
Hatib ibn Abi Balta'a

00:53:56.340 --> 00:53:59.340
was the man who killed this utbah

00:53:59.340 --> 00:54:00.340
ibn Abi Waqqas

00:54:00.340 --> 00:54:03.340
who had thrown a rock on Rasulullah sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:54:03.340 --> 00:54:06.340
when the Muslims retreated to part of the mount

00:54:06.340 --> 00:54:09.340
as the mount subhanallah was behind them

00:54:09.340 --> 00:54:11.340
they retreated to part of the mount

00:54:11.340 --> 00:54:13.340
and the Prophet sallallahu alaihi wasallam

00:54:13.340 --> 00:54:15.340
was being treated by some of his companions

00:54:15.340 --> 00:54:17.340
his daughter Fatima radiallahu anha

00:54:17.340 --> 00:54:20.340
some of the females of the sahabiyat

00:54:20.340 --> 00:54:21.340
had come from a distance

00:54:21.340 --> 00:54:22.340
they were assisting with the water

00:54:22.340 --> 00:54:24.340
and they were assisting in trying to

00:54:24.340 --> 00:54:26.340
help the wounded and so on

00:54:26.340 --> 00:54:27.340
they were there

00:54:27.340 --> 00:54:30.340
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala revealed verses

00:54:30.340 --> 00:54:33.340
Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala revealed verses

00:54:33.340 --> 00:54:34.340
that were so powerful

00:54:34.340 --> 00:54:38.340
70 of the Muslims had been martyred approximately

00:54:38.340 --> 00:54:41.340
one figure takes it a little bit higher than 70

00:54:41.340 --> 00:54:43.340
and from amongst the disbelievers

00:54:43.340 --> 00:54:46.340
between 20 and 40 of them were martyred

00:54:46.340 --> 00:54:47.340
and subhanallah

00:54:47.340 --> 00:54:50.340
the verses revealed by Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:55:00.340 --> 00:55:02.340
what happened to you

00:55:02.340 --> 00:55:04.340
the day the two armies met in Uhud

00:55:04.340 --> 00:55:05.340
was by the will of Allah

00:55:05.340 --> 00:55:08.340
in order to know who are the true believers

00:55:12.340 --> 00:55:14.340
and in order to know the hypocrites

00:55:26.340 --> 00:55:29.340
and the hypocrites were told

00:55:29.340 --> 00:55:32.340
come and fight in the cause of Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala

00:55:33.340 --> 00:55:35.340
Allah says they responded

00:55:35.340 --> 00:55:37.340
had we known how to fight

00:55:37.340 --> 00:55:39.340
we would have been right behind you

00:55:39.340 --> 00:55:42.340
and this was the exposure of Abdullah ibn Ubayy ibn Salun

00:55:42.340 --> 00:55:44.340
he went back with so many men

00:55:53.340 --> 00:55:56.340
on that day they were closer to disbelief

00:55:56.340 --> 00:55:59.340
these hypocrites than they ever were to Iman

00:55:59.340 --> 00:56:01.340
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala sent verses

00:56:01.340 --> 00:56:02.340
saying

00:56:08.340 --> 00:56:12.340
Allah has indeed fulfilled his promise to you

00:56:12.340 --> 00:56:15.340
when you were executing these people one after the other

00:56:15.340 --> 00:56:16.340
you see how it started

00:56:16.340 --> 00:56:18.340
it started in a way where

00:56:18.340 --> 00:56:21.340
the flag bearers of the mushriks were lost

00:56:21.340 --> 00:56:23.340
or their lives were lost one after the other

00:56:23.340 --> 00:56:26.340
and there was chaos in the ranks of the disbelievers

00:56:26.340 --> 00:56:27.340
then Allah says

00:56:31.340 --> 00:56:40.340
Arabic

00:56:40.340 --> 00:56:43.340
until a point when you disobeyed

00:56:43.340 --> 00:56:47.340
and you had become discouraged

00:56:47.340 --> 00:56:51.340
because of your disobedience to Allah's messenger

00:56:51.340 --> 00:56:53.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:56:53.340 --> 00:56:55.340
after you saw that

00:56:55.340 --> 00:56:56.340
which you loved

00:56:56.340 --> 00:56:58.340
what was it that they loved

00:56:58.340 --> 00:57:01.340
oh the booty of the war they saw so much of it

00:57:01.340 --> 00:57:02.340
and they started rushing

00:57:02.340 --> 00:57:05.340
so Allah is admonishing the archers to say

00:57:05.340 --> 00:57:09.340
the reason why you had suffered loss

00:57:09.340 --> 00:57:12.340
is because of your disobedience of the messenger

00:57:12.340 --> 00:57:14.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:57:14.340 --> 00:57:16.340
then Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:57:24.340 --> 00:57:27.340
from amongst you there are some who wanted this worldly life

00:57:27.340 --> 00:57:30.340
and some who were prepared for the life after death

00:57:30.340 --> 00:57:31.340
Allah says

00:57:47.340 --> 00:57:49.340
then by Allah's mercy

00:57:49.340 --> 00:57:52.340
did Allah cause them to go away

00:57:52.340 --> 00:57:55.340
so the mushriks of Makkah went away

00:57:55.340 --> 00:57:57.340
and Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala says

00:57:57.340 --> 00:57:59.340
Allah then forgave the believers

00:57:59.340 --> 00:58:02.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us from His mercy

00:58:02.340 --> 00:58:04.340
Abu Sufyan as he was leaving

00:58:04.340 --> 00:58:06.340
he looks at the messenger

00:58:06.340 --> 00:58:08.340
sallallahu alayhi wasallam

00:58:08.340 --> 00:58:09.340
and he uttered a statement

00:58:09.340 --> 00:58:11.340
he says

00:58:11.340 --> 00:58:13.340
a day for a day

00:58:13.340 --> 00:58:15.340
which means you attacked us on Badr

00:58:15.340 --> 00:58:17.340
today we have attacked you here

00:58:17.340 --> 00:58:18.340
and as they were leaving

00:58:18.340 --> 00:58:20.340
they said you will find from your dead

00:58:20.340 --> 00:58:23.340
those who have been cut up and ripped up

00:58:23.340 --> 00:58:26.340
after they were executed

00:58:26.340 --> 00:58:28.340
I did not instruct this

00:58:28.340 --> 00:58:30.340
they did it themselves

00:58:30.340 --> 00:58:31.340
so don't hold it against us

00:58:31.340 --> 00:58:34.340
but we will return next year

00:58:34.340 --> 00:58:36.340
we will meet and we will fight again

00:58:36.340 --> 00:58:39.340
same time at a place known as Badr

00:58:39.340 --> 00:58:42.340
these were the last words of Abu Sufyan as he left

00:58:42.340 --> 00:58:44.340
and inshallah tomorrow we will see

00:58:44.340 --> 00:58:47.340
what was the aftermath of this battle of Uhud

00:58:47.340 --> 00:58:50.340
where the Muslims did not win

00:58:50.340 --> 00:58:52.340
but the kuffar did not win either

00:58:52.340 --> 00:58:55.340
had they won they would have gone into Madina Munawwara

00:58:55.340 --> 00:58:57.340
but they did not enter Madina Munawwara

00:58:57.340 --> 00:58:58.340
they left from there

00:58:58.340 --> 00:59:03.340
because they found even those who had remained of the Muslims

00:59:03.340 --> 00:59:06.340
were fighting like brave warriors

00:59:06.340 --> 00:59:09.340
may Allah subhanahu wa ta'ala grant us goodness

00:59:09.340 --> 00:59:12.340
perhaps tomorrow we will see a little bit more what happened

00:59:12.340 --> 00:59:14.340
and thereafter draw some lessons for us all

00:59:14.340 --> 00:59:15.340
until we meet again

00:59:15.340 --> 00:59:18.340
wa salallahu wa sallam wa baraka ala nabina Muhammad

00:59:18.340 --> 00:59:19.340
subhanallahi wa bi hamdihi

00:59:19.340 --> 00:59:20.340
subhanaka allahum wa bi hamdiki

00:59:20.340 --> 00:59:22.340
ash-hadu an la ilaha illa anta

00:59:22.340 --> 00:59:24.340
astaghfiruka wa natubu ilayh
